var book = {
	"name": "2 Syiem",
	"numChapters": 25,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ynda la ïap u Ahab, ki Moab ki la ïaleh pyrshah ïa ki Israel.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Ahasaïah u la hap lyngba ka jingkhang ïit ha ka kamra haneng ka jong u kaba ha Samaria, bad u la pang: te u la phah ki nongkit-ktien, bad u la ong ha ki, “Khie leit ïakylli ha u Belsebul u blei ka Ekron, la ngan koit ne em na kane ka jingpang.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hynrei, u angel U Trai u la ong ha u Elijah u nong Tishbi, “To ïeng, leit kiew ban ïashem ïa ki nongkit-ktien u syiem ka Samaria, bad to ong ha ki, ‘Sha hana bymdon U Blei ha Israel, ba phi leit ïakylli ha u Belsebul u blei ka Ekron?’",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Namar kata te, kumne ong U Trai, ‘Men ym khie shuh na kata ka jingthiah sha kaba me la leit kiew, hynrei, men ïap shisha.’ ” Bad u Elijah u la leit noh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te kita ki nongkit-ktien ki la leit phai pat sha u, te u la ong ha ki, “Na ka balei ba phi la ïawan phai pat?”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ki te ki la ong ha u, “La wan kiew uwei u briew ban ïashem bad ngi, bad u la ong ha ngi, ‘Khie leit phai pat sha uta u syiem uba la phah ïa phi, bad ong ha u, “Kumne ong U Trai: Sha hana bymdon U Blei ha Israel, ba me la phah ïakylli ha u Belsebul u blei ka Ekron? namar kata, men ym hiar shuh na kata ka jingthiah sha kaba me la leit kiew, hynrei, men ïap shisha.” ’ ”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u la ong ha ki, “Uba kumno uta u briew uba la wan kiew ban ïashem bad phi, bad uba la ïathuh ha phi ïa kine ki ktien?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ki te ki la ïathuh ha u, “U la long u briew uba mih 'ñiuh sameb bad uba panpoh da ka jingpanpoh snieh ha ka syngkai.” U la ong te, “U dei u Elijah u nong Tishbi.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem u la phah sha u ïa u rangbah sanphew lem bad la ki sanphew ngut. Bad u la leit kiew sha u: te ha khmih, u la shong halor u lum rit. Bad u la kren ha u, “A u briew jong U Blei, u syiem u la ong, ‘To hiar noh.’ ”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U Elijah te u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha uta u rangbah sanphew, “Lada nga long u briew jong U Blei, to kan hiar ka ding na bneng, bad kan bam duh ïa me bad ïa ki sanphew ngut jong me.” Te la hiar ka ding na bneng, bad ka la bam duh ïa u bad ki sanphew ngut jong u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u la phah pat ha u sa uwei pat u rangbah sanphew lem bad la ki sanphew ngut. Bad u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha u, “A u briew jong U Blei, kumne u syiem u la ong, To hiar noh kloi.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U Elijah te u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha ki, “Lada nga long u briew jong U Blei, to kan hiar ka ding na bneng, bad kan bam duh ïa me bad ïa ki sanphew ngut jong me.” Te ka ding U Blei ka la hiar na bneng, bad ka la bam duh ïa u bad ïa ki sanphew ngut jong u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u la phah pat sa ïa u rangbah ka sanphew ka balai, lem bad la ki sanphew ngut. Te uta u rangbah sanphew u balai u la leit kiew, bad haba u la poi u la dem khrup ïa la ki khohsiew ha khmat u Elijah, bad u la kyrpad ïa u, bad u la ong ruh ha u, “A u briew jong U Blei, nga duwai ïa me, to shah ba ka jingim jong nga, lem bad ka jingim jong kine ki sanphew ngut ki shakri jong me, kin long kordor ha khmat jong me.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ha khmih, la hiar ka ding na bneng bad ka la bam duh ïa kita ki ar ngut ki rangbah sanphew kiba mynshuwa lem bad ki sanphew ngut jong ki: hynrei, mynta to ai ba ka jingim jong nga kan long kordor ha khmat jong me.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u angel U Trai u la ong ha u Elijah, “To leit hiar bad u: wat sheptieng ïa u.” Te haba u la ïeng u la leit hiar bad u sha uta u syiem.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u la ong ha u, “Kumne ong U Trai, ‘Namar kumba me la phah nongkit-ktien ban ïakylli ha u Belsebul u blei ka Ekron, sha bymdon U Blei ha Israel ban ïakylli ïa ka ktien jong u? namar kata, men ym khie shuh na kata ka jingthiah sha kaba me la leit kiew, hynrei, men ïap shisha.’ ”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kumta, u la ïap katba kum ka ktien U Trai kaba u Elijah u la lah kren. Te u Jehoram u la sdang ban synshar ha ka jaka jong u ha ka snem ka ba-ar jong u Jehoram u khun u Jehoshaphat u syiem ka Judah; namar um shym la don khun shynrang.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Ahasaïah kiba u la leh ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ki Israel?"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba U Trai un sa rah noh ïa u Elijah ha ka 'erïong sha bneng, u Elijah u la leit bad u Elisha na Gilgal.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Elijah u la ong ha u Elisha, “To sah hangne, nga kyrpad ïa me; naba U Trai u la phah ïa nga haduh Bethel.” U Elisha te u la ong, “Katba im U Trai, bad katba im ka mynsiem jong me, ngan ym iehnoh ïa me.” Kumta, ki la ïaleit hiar sha Bethel.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te ki khun ki nongïathuhlypa kiba ha Bethel ki la ïawan ha u Elisha, bad ki la ong ha u, “Me tip ba U Trai un rah noh na me ïa u kynrad jong me ha kane ka sngi?” Te u la ong, “Ho-oid, nga tip ïa kata; phi to sngap jar.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Elijah u la ong ha u, “Ko Elisha, to sah hangne, nga kyrpad ïa me; naba U Trai u la phah ïa nga sha Jerikho.” U te u la ong, “Katba im U Trai, bad katba im ka mynsiem jong me, ngan ym iehnoh ïa me.” Kumta, ki la ïapoi sha Jerikho.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ki khun ki nongïathuhlypa kiba ha Jerikho ki la ïawan hajan u Elisha, bad ki la ong ha u, “Me tip ba U Trai un rah noh ïa u kynrad jong me na me ha kane ka sngi?” U te u la ïathuh, “Ho-oid, nga tip ïa kata; phi to sngap jar.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u Elijah u la ong ha u, “Sah hangne nga kyrpad ïa me; naba U Trai u la phah ïa nga sha Jordan.” U te u la ong, “Katba im U Trai, bad katba im ka mynsiem jong me, ngan ym iehnoh ïa me.” Bad baroh ar ngut ki la nang leit.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad sanphew ngut ki rangbah na ki khun u nongïathuhlypa ki la leit, bad ki ïeng marpyrshah ïa ki na sha jngai: ki te baroh ar ngut ki la ïeng harud ka Jordan.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Elijah u la shim ïa la ka barandi, bad u la kli lang ïa ka, bad u la shoh ïa ki um, bad ki la ïakhlad shane bad shatai, kumta, ma ki baroh ar ngut ki la leit poi sha shiliang na ka 'dewrkhiang.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ynda ki la poi sha shiliang, u Elijah u la ong ha u Elisha, “To pan kaei ba ngan leh ïa me, shuwa ban shim ïa nga na me.” Bad u Elisha u la ong, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to ai ba ar bynta na ka mynsiem jong me kan long halor jong nga.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U te u la ong, “Me la pan ïa kaba eh: la kumta ruh, lada men ïohi ïa nga haba shim ïa nga na me kan long kumta ïa me; hynrei, lada em, kan ym long kumta.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te katba ki la nang ïaïaid, bad ïakren, ha khmih, la paw ka kali ding, bad ki kulai ding, kiba la pynïakhlad ïa ki baroh ar ngut; bad u Elijah u la leit kiew ha ka 'erïong sha bneng.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u Elisha u la ïohi, bad u la pyrta, “Ko kpa, ko kpa jong nga, ka kali Israel, bad ki nongshong kulai jong u!” bad um ïohi shuh ïa u: bad u la bat ïa la ki jaiñkup, bad u la kad ïa ki lyngkhot lyngkhot.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U la shim ruh ïa ka barandi u Elijah kaba la hap na u, te haba u la leit phai, u la ïeng harud ka Jordan.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u la shim ïa ka barandi u Elijah kaba la hap na u, bad u la shoh ïa ki um, bad u la ong, “Hangno long U Trai, U Blei jong u Elijah?” Te ynda u ruh u la shoh ïa ki um, ki la ïakhlad shane bad shatai: bad u Elisha u la leit sha shiliang.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ynda ki khun ki nongïathuhlypa kiba ha Jerikho marpyrshah ïa u ki la ïohi ïa u, ki la ong, “Ka mynsiem u Elijah ka sah ha u Elisha.” Bad ki la wan ïashem bad u, bad ki la dem ngon ha khmat jong u.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ki la ïa-ong ha u, “Ha khmih, don lem bad ki shakri jong me sanphew ngut ki rangbah ki bakhlaiñ; ngi kyrpad ïa me, to shah ba kin leit wad ïa u kynrad jong me: ïoh ba lehse U Mynsiem U Trai u la rah ïa u, bad u pynhiar ïa u ha uno uno u lum, lane ha kano kano ka them.” Bad u la ong, “Phin ym phah.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te ynda ki la ïaipynbor ïa u, haduh ba u la lehrain, u la ong, “To phah.” Namar kata, ki la ïaphah sanphew ngut; bad ki la wad ïa u, lai sngi, hynrei, kim shym la shem ïa u.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ki la ïawan phai pat sha u, katba u dang sah ha Jerikho; bad u la ong ha ki, “Ngam shym la ong ha phi, ‘Wat leit?’ ”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te ki rangbah ka shnong ki la ong ha u Elisha, “Ha khmih, ngi kyrpad ïa me, ka jaka kane ka shnong ka long kaba itynnad, kumba ïohi u kynrad jong nga: hynrei, ka um ka basniew, bad ka khyndew kaba lyngki.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u la ong, “To wallam ha nga uwei u khiew thymmai, bad buh mluh ha u.” Bad ki la wallam ïa u ha u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u la leit sha kaba mih ki um, bad u la bet ïa kata ka mluh hangta, bad u la ong ruh, “Kumne ong U Trai, ‘Nga la pynbha ïa kine ki um: kan ym long shuh nangta ka jingïap lane ka jinglyngki.’ ”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kumta, la pynbha ïa kita ki um haduh kane ka sngi, kat kum ka ktien u Elisha kaba u la kren.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u la leit kiew nangta sha Bethel: te katba u dang leit ha lynti, la mih ki khynnah na shnong, bad ki la krenbeiñ ïa u, bad ki la ong ha u, “Khie me, uba synlen khlieh; khie me, uba synlen khlieh.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te haba u la kyrtiang u la ïohi ïa ki, bad u la tim ïa ki ha ka kyrteng U Trai. Bad la mih ruh ar tylli ki dngiem kynthei na khlaw, bad la tar na ki, sawphew ar ngut ki khynnah.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Nangta te u la leit sha u lum Karmel, bad nangta u la wan phai sha Samaria."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Jehoram u khun u Ahab u la sdang ban synshar halor ki Israel ha Samaria ha ka snem ka bakhatphra jong u Jehoshaphat u syiem ka Judah, bad u la synshar khat-ar snem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai; hynrei, ym kum u kpa jong u, bad kum ka kmie jong u: namar u la pynduh noh ïa ka dur u Baal kaba u kpa jong u, u la thaw.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Pynban, u la snoh ha ki pop u Jeroboam u khun u Nebat, da kaba u la pynleh pop ïa ki Israel; um shym kynriah na kita.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te u Mesha u syiem ki Moab u la long u nongri blang; bad u ju ai ha u syiem ki Israel u shñiuh ki khun langbrot shispah hajar, bad u jong ki langbrot shynrang shispah hajar.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ynda la ïap u Ahab, u syiem ki Moab, u la ïaleh pyrshah ïa u syiem ki Israel.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u syiem Jehoram u la mih na Samaria ha kata ka por, bad u la ïalum lang ïa ki Israel baroh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te haba u la leit u la phah ha u Jehoshaphat u syiem ka Judah, u da ong, “U syiem ki Moab u la ïaleh pyrshah ïa nga: men leit bad nga ban ïaleh thma ïa ki Moab?” U la ong te, “Ngan leit keiñ: nga long kumjuh kum me, ki briew jong nga ruh kum ki briew jong me, ki kulai jong nga ruh kum ki jong me.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u la ong, “Na kano ka lynti ngin ïaleit?” U la ïathuh, “Na ka lynti jong ka khlaw Edom.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kumta, u syiem ki Israel u la leit, bad u syiem ka Judah, bad u syiem ki Edom de: bad ki la ïaid tawiar hynñiew sngi lynti: bad ym don um ïa u paidïapom, lymne ïa ki mrad kiba bud ïa ki.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u syiem ki Israel u la ong, “Waw! naba U Trai u la khot lang ïa kine lai ngut ki syiem ban ai noh ïa ki ha ka kti ki Moab.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hynrei, u Jehoshaphat u la ong, “Ym don hangne u nongïathuhlypa jong U Trai, ba ngi lah ban ïakylli ha U Trai da u?” Bad uwei na ki shakri u syiem ki Israel u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “U Elisha u khun u Shaphat u don hangne, uba ju theh um ha ki kti u Elijah.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Jehoshaphat u la ong, “Ka ktien U Trai ka don bad u.” Kumta u syiem ki Israel bad u Jehoshaphat bad u syiem ki Edom ki la ïaleit hiar sha u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Elisha u la ong ha u syiem ki Israel, “Nga don aïu bad me? Khie leit sha ki nongïathuhlypa u kpa jong me, bad sha ki nongïathuhlypa ka kmie jong me.” Te u syiem ki Israel u la ong ha u, “Em: naba U Trai u la khot lang ïa kine ki lai ngut ki syiem ban ai noh ïa ki ha ka kti ki Moab.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u Elisha u la ong, “Katba im U Trai ki paid, ha khmat uba nga ïeng, da shisha, lada kam long ba nga burom ïa ka khmat u Jehoshaphat u syiem ka Judah, ngan ym da khmih sha me, lane ïohi ïa me.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hynrei, to wallam ha nga uwei u nongtem.” Te haba uta u nongtem u la tem, ka kti U Trai ka la wan ha u.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u la ong, “Kumne u ong U Trai, ‘Pyndap ïa kane ka them da ki kharai.’",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Naba kumne u ong U Trai, ‘Phin ym ïohi ïa ka lyer lymne phin ym ïohi ïa u slap, pynban, kata ka them kan dap da ka um: bad phin sa ïadih, ma phi ruh bad ki jingri jong phi bad ki mrad jong phi.’",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te kane ka long tang kaba rit ha khmat U Trai: un ai ruh ïa ki Moab ha ka kti jong phi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad phin jop ïa ka shnong baroh ba la ker, bad ka shnong babha baroh, bad phin khet ïa u dieng babha baroh, bad phin set ïa ki umpohliew baroh, bad pynsniew ïa ka khyndew babha baroh da ki maw.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ha kaba mynstep, hamar ka por kata ka jingainguh, ha khmih, la wan ka um na ka lynti Edom, bad ka ri ka la dap da ka um.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te haba ki Moab baroh ki la ïohsngew ba kita ki syiem ki la wan ïaleh thma ïa ki, ki la ïalum lang, baroh kat kiba lah ban kieng atiar, bad palat ruh, bad ki la ïeng hamar ka pud.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te ki la khie dang step kum lashai, bad ka sngi ka la tyngshaiñ halor kata ka um, bad ki Moab ki la ïohi ïa kata ka um kaba marpyrshah ïa ki ba ka saw kum ka snam:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> ki la ong te, “Kane keiñ ka snam; ïa kita ki syiem shisha la pynduh khoit, bad ki la ïa-pynïap paralok: namar kata te, ko Moab, ïa, sha ka jinglute.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te ynda ki la poi sha ka dara ki Israel, ki Israel ki la khie joit bad ki la pom ïa ki Moab, kumta, ki la phet ïap na khmat jong ki: bad ki la nang ïaid sha ka ri ki da pom ïa ki Moab.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ki la pynkyllon noh ïa ki nongbah; bad ha ka khyndew ka babha baroh man la u briew u la shat ïa u maw, bad la pyndap ïa ka; bad ïa ki umpohliew baroh ki la set, bad ïa u dieng babha baroh ki la khet: haduh ha Kir-hareseth tang hangta ki la iehnoh ïa ki maw jong ka; hynrei, ki nongkawang maw ki la ïaid sawdong ïa ka, bad ki la jop ïa ka.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te haba u syiem ki Moab u la ïohi ba ka thma ka la jur eh ïa u, u la shim lem bad u hynñiewspah ngut ki rangbah kiba rah wait, ban tur lyngba haduh u syiem ki Edom: hynrei, kim lah.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ynda kumta, u la shim ïa la u khun nyngkong uba la dei ban synshar ha ka jaka jong u, bad u la ainguh ïa u kum ka jingainguh thang halor ka kynroh. Te la don ka jingbitar bajur pyrshah ïa ki Israel: kumta ki la iehnoh ïa u, bad ki la leit phai pat sha la ka jong ka ri."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te kawei ka kynthei na ki tnga ki khun ki nongïathuhlypa ka la pyrta ha u Elisha, ka da ong, “U shakri jong me u tnga jong nga u la ïap: bad me tip ba u shakri jong me u la sheptieng ïa U Trai: bad u nongshah ram u la wan ban ring mraw ha u ïa ki khun shynrang jong nga baroh ar ngut.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U Elisha te u la ong ha ka, “Ngan leh aïu na ka bynta jong pha? to ïathuh ïa nga, pha don aïu ha ïing?” Ka la ong te, “Ka shakri jong me kam don ei ei ha ïing, hynrei, tang ka umphniang shi khiew.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u la ong, “Khie leit pan khiew kylliang na ki paramarjan jong pha baroh, ki khiew ki bathylli keiñ; pan ym khyndiat.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad phan rung shapoh, te ynda pha la khang ïa ka jingkhang hadien jong pha bad ki khun jong pha, to phylliew ha kita ki khiew baroh; bad ïa uta uba la dap, phan buh kyrpang.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kumta, ka la leit noh na u, bad ka la khang hadien jong ka bad ki khun jong ka; ki la wallam ïa ki khiew ha ka, bad ka la phylliew.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ynda la dap kita ki khiew, ka la ong ha la u khun, “To wallam khiew shuh.” Bad u la ïathuh ha ka, “Ym don khiew shuh.” Bad ka umphniang ka la sangeh noh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ynda kumta, ka la wan ïathuh ha u briew jong U Blei. U te u la ong ha ka, “Khie leit die ïa kata ka umphniang, bad to siew ïa la ka ram, bad ïa kaba sah tam to bam ma pha bad ki khun jong pha.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te ka la jia ha kawei ka sngi, ba u Elisha u la leit poi sha Shunem, bad hangta la don ka kynthei bakhraw batri; bad ka la pynbor ïa u ban bam jingbam. Bad ka la long kumta, ba katba u leit poi nangta u ju leit rung shata ban bam jingbam.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ka la ong ha u tnga jong ka, “Ha khmih, nga sngewthuh ba une u long u briew bakhuid jong U Blei, uba ïaid na ngi borabor.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Nga kyrpad ïa me, to ngin ïathaw iwei i kamra rit ha ka kynroh; bad ngin ïabuh ïa u hangta ka jingthiah, bad ka miej, bad ka mula, bad ka dieng pynïeng sharak: te kan long haba u wan poi sha ngi, ba un leit rung shata.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ka la jia ha kawei ka sngi, ba u la wan poi shata, bad u la leit rung sha ita i kamra bad u la thiah hangta.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U la ong te ha u Gehasi u shakri jong u, “To khot ïa kane ka nong Shunem.” Te ynda u la lah khot ïa ka, ka la ïeng ha khmat jong u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u la ong ha u, “To ong ha ka, Ha khmih, pha la leh donburom ïa ngi da kane ka jingsumar baroh; aïu ka dei ban leh ïa pha? Pha kwah ban kren na ka bynta jong pha ha u syiem lane ha u rangbah ki nongïapom?” Te ka la ïathuh, “Nga shong hapdeng la ki jong ki briew.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U te u la ong, “Aïu ka dei ban leh ïa ka?” Bad u Gehasi u la ïathuh, “Shisha kam don khun shynrang, bad u tnga jong ka u la tymmen.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> U la ong te, “Khot ïa ka.” Te ynda u la khot ïa ka, ka la ïeng ha ka jingkhang.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u la ong ha ka, “Kum ha kane ka aïom, ynda ka por ka la poi biang, phan kynthup khun shynrang.” Ka te ka la ong, “Em, ko kynrad, me u briew jong U Blei, wat lamler ïa ka shakri jong me.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te kata ka kynthei ka la punkhun, bad ka la kha khun shynrang hamar kata ka aïom, haba ka la poi biang ka por, kumba u Elisha u la lah ong ha ka.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te ynda uta u khynnah u la san, ka la jia ha kawei ka sngi, ba u la leit shabar sha u kpa jong u sha ki nongot Kew.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u la ong ha la u kpa, “Waw ka khlieh jong nga, ka khlieh jong nga.” U la ong te ha u shakri jong u, “To leit bah ïa u sha la ka kmie.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ynda u la shim ïa u, bad wallam ïa u sha la ka kmie, u la shong ha ki khohsiew jong ka haduh shiteng sngi, ynda kumta te, u la ïap.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te ka la leit kiew, bad ka la buh ïa u halor ka jingthiah uta u briew jong U Blei, bad ynda ka la khang ïa ka jingkhang, ka la leit noh.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad ka la khot ïa u tnga jong ka, bad ka la ong, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, phah ha nga uwei na ki shakri, bad kawei na ki kadda, ba ngan leit mareh sha u briew u jong U Blei, bad wan phai pat.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> U la ong te, “Namar balei phan leit sha u mynta? kam long u bnai thymmai lane ka Sabbaton.” Bad ka la ong, “Koit.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ynda kumta, ka la teh jin ïa ka kadda, bad ka la ong ha la u shakri, “To da nang pynmareh, bad nang leit; wat pyntud ïa ka jingleit, lymda nga hukum ïa me.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kumta, ka la leit, bad ka la poi haduh u briew jong U Blei ha u lum Karmel. Te haba u briew jong U Blei u la ïohi ïa ka na sha jngai, u la ong ha u Gehasi u shakri jong u, “Ha khmih, hangtai kata ka nong Shunem:",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> nga kyrpad ïa me, to phet ban tan ïa ka, bad to kylli ïa ka, ‘Kumno, pha koit? U tnga jong pha u koit? Uta u khun jong pha de u koit?’ ” Ka la ïathuh te, “Koit.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te ynda ka la poi ha uta u briew jong U Blei ha uta u lum, ka la bat na ki kjat jong u. Bad u Gehasi u la wan hajan ban beh noh ïa ka; hynrei, uta u briew jong U Blei u la ong, “To ieh ïa ka: namar ka mynsiem jong ka, ka khuslai hapoh jong ka; bad U Trai u la buhrieh ïa kata na nga, bad um shym la ïathuh ha nga.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ynda kumta, ka la ong, “Nga la kwah ne em ïa u khun na u kynrad jong nga? Ngam shym ong, ‘Wat shukor ïa nga?’ ”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ynda kumta, u la ong ha u Gehasi, “To panpoh ïa ka syngkai, bad to rah ïa u diengduh jong nga ha la ka kti, bad leit noh: lada me ïashem badno badno, wat ïakhublei ïa u; bad lada uno uno u khublei ïa me, wat phai ktien ïa u: bad to buh ïa u diengduh jong nga halor ka khmat uta u khynnah.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te ka kmie uta u khynnah ka la ong, “Katba im U Trai, bad katba im ka mynsiem jong me, ngan ym iehnoh ïa me.” U te u la ïeng, bad u la bud ïa ka.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te u Gehasi u la nang leit ha shuwa jong ki, bad u la buh ïa uta u diengduh halor ka khmat uta u khynnah; hynrei, ym don ka jingsawa, lymne kaba sngew. Namar kata, u la leit phai ban ïashem ïa u, bad u la ïathuh ha u, u da ong, “U khynnah um khih satia.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te ynda u Elisha u la poi ha kata ka ïing, ha khmih, u khynnah u la ïap, bad la buh ïa u ha ka jingthiah jong u.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Namar kata, u la rung shapoh, bad u la khyrdep ïa ka jingkhang tang ma ki ar ngut hi, bad u la duwai ha U Trai.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te haba u la kiew, u la dem halor uta u khynnah, bad u la pyndei ïa la ka shyntur ha ka shyntur jong u, bad ïa la ki khmat ha ki khmat jong u, bad ïa la ki kti ha ki kti jong u: bad u la pyiar ïa lade halor jong u; bad ka doh uta u khynnah ka la syaid.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ynda kumta, u la phai, bad u la ïaid hapoh ïing shi wat shane bad shi wat shatai; te haba u la kiew, u la kner ïa lade halor jong u: bad uta u khynnah u la synriah hynñiew sien, bad uta u khynnah u la peit ki khmat.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te u la khot ïa u Gehasi, bad u la ong, “To khot ïa kane ka nong Shunem.” Kumta, u la khot ïa ka. Te ynda ka la wan rung sha u, u la ong, “To shim ïa la u khun.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te ka la leit shapoh, bad ka la dem ha ki kjat jong u, bad ka la dem ngon haduh khyndew; te haba ka la shim ïa la u khun, ka la mih noh.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Te u Elisha u la wan poi pat sha Gilgal: bad la don ka 'nemsniew ha ka ri: bad ki khun ki nongïathuhlypa ki la dang ïashong ha khmat jong u: u la ong te ha la u shakri, “Tiew u khiew heh, bad shet syrwa jhur ïa ki khun ki nongïathuhlypa.”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te uwei u la leit sha lum ban kheit jhur, bad u la shem uwei u dieng Waiñ khlaw, bad u la kheit na u ki jyrmi khlaw shi kynthup, bad ynda u la poi, u la dkhat ïa ki ha uta u khiew syrwa: naba kim ithuh ïa ki.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Kumta, ki la theh, ïa kita ki briew ban ïabam. Te katba ki dang ïabam na kata ka syrwa, ki la ïapyrta, bad ki la ong, “A u briew jong U Blei, ka don ka jingïap hapoh u khiew.” Bad kim ïalah bam na ka.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Hynrei, u la ong, “Wallam moida te.” Bad u la ber ïa u ha uta u khiew; bad u la ong, “To theh ïa ki briew, ba kin ïabam.” Bad ym shym la don jingsniew ha uta u khiew.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Te la wan uwei u briew na Baal-shelishah, bad u la wallam kpu ïa u briew jong U Blei na ki soh nyngkong, arphew tylli ki kpu Barli, bad u soh Kew im ha la ka byrni. U la ong te, “To ai ha kine ki briew ba kin ïabam.”",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Te u shakri jong u, u la ong, “Kumno ngan buh ïa ine ha khmat shispah ngut ki briew?” Hynrei, u la ong, “To ai ha ki briew, ba kin bam; naba kumne ong U Trai, Kin bam bad kin ïa-pyntam ruh.”",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Kumta, u la buh ha khmat jong ki, bad ki la ïabam, bad ki la ïa-pyntam ruh, katba kum ka ktien U Trai."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Naaman, u rangbah u paidïapom u syiem ka Syria, u la long u briew bakhraw ha khmat u kynrad jong u, bad uba donburom, namar da u, U Trai u la ai ka jingjop ha ka Syria: u la long ruh u briew bakhrawbor eh, hynrei, uba sa 'ñiangthohlieh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ki Syria ki la leit mih shi kynhun kynhun, bad ki la ring mraw na ka ri Israel kawei ka samla; bad kata ka la shakri ïa ka tnga u Naaman.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ka la ong te ha la ka kynrad, “A ban da u kynrad jong nga u don bad u nongïathuhlypa uba ha Samaria! te un da pynkhiah ïa u na u 'ñiangthohlieh jong u.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te uwei u la leit rung, bad u la ïathuh ha u kynrad jong u, u da ong, “Kumta kumta ka ong kata ka khynnah kaba na ri Israel.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u syiem ka Syria u la ong, “Khie, to leit, bad ngan phah da ka shithi ha u syiem ki Israel.” Kumta, u la leit, bad u la shim bad u, shiphew ki talent rupa, bad hynriew hajar shekel ka ksiar, bad shiphew riam ki jaiñkup jaiñsem.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u la wallam ïa kata ka shithi ha u syiem ki Israel, u da ong, “Te ynda kane ka shithi ka la wan poi ha me, ha khmih, nga la phah ïa u Naaman u shakri jong nga ha me, ba men pynkhiah ïa u na u 'ñiangthohlieh jong u.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te haba u syiem ki Israel u la lah pule ïa kata ka shithi, u la kad ïa la ki jaiñ, bad u la ong, “Nga long U Blei mo, u ban pynïap bad u ban pynim, ba une u briew u phah ha nga ban pynkoit ïa u briew na u 'ñiangthohlieh jong u? Hynrei, nga kyrpad ïa phi, to pyrkhat, bad to khmih, kumno u wad daw ban ïakajia bad nga.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te ynda u Elisha u briew jong U Blei u la ïohsngew ba u syiem ki Israel u la kad ïa la ki jaiñ, u la phah ha u syiem, u da ong, “Balei ba me leit kad ïa la ki jaiñ? ieh un wan mynta sha nga, te un ïoh tip ba don u nongïathuhlypa ha Israel.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kumta, u Naaman u la wan lem bad la ki kulai bad ki kali jong u ruh, bad u la ïeng ha ka jingkhang ka ïing u Elisha.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U Elisha te u la phah u nonglam-ktien ha u, u da ong, “Khie leit sum ha Jordan hynñiew sien, bad ka doh jong me kan wan biang ha me, bad men long khuid.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hynrei, u Naaman u la bitar, bad u la leit noh, u la ong ruh, “Ha khmih, nga la mut, shisha un wan mih sha nga bad un ïeng, bad un khot ïa ka kyrteng U Trai U Blei jong u, bad un kaweh ïa la ka kti halor kata ka jaka, bad un pynkhiah ïa uta u bapang 'ñiangthohlieh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hato ka Abana bad ka Pharpar, ki wah ka Damaskos, kim long kham bha ban ïa ki um ka Israel baroh? Ngam lah ban sum ha ki, bad ban khuid?” Kumta, u la phai bad u la leit noh da ka jingbitar lep.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ki shakri jong u ki la wan hajan, bad ki la kren ha u, ki ong ruh, “Ko kpa, lada uta u nongïathuhlypa u la hukum ïa me ban leh kaei kaei kaba khraw, men ym da la leh ïa kata? Sa katno lei lei, haba u shu ong ha me, ‘To sum, bad to long khuid?’ ”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ynda kumta, u la leit hiar, bad u la sum hynñiew sien ha Jordan, katba kum ka jingong u briew jong U Blei: bad ka doh jong u ka la wan biang kum ka doh u khunlung, bad u la khuid.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u la leit phai sha u briew jong U Blei, ma u bad kiba bad u baroh, ki la wan, bad ki la ïeng ha khmat jong u: bad u la ong, “Ha khmih, mynta nga tip ba ym don U Blei ha ka pyrthei baroh, hynrei, tang ha Israel: nga kyrpad ïa me te namar kata, to shim ka jingai sngewbha na u shakri jong me.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hynrei, u la ong, “Katba im U Trai, ha khmat uba nga ïeng, ngan ym shim ei ei.” Bad u la pynbor ïa u ban shim ïa ka; hynrei, um treh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u Naaman u la ong, “Lym kumta ruh, hynrei, nga kyrpad ïa me, to shah ban ai ha u shakri jong me ka khyndew ar kit ki kadda; namar u shakri jong me un ym ainguh naduh mynta ka jingainguh thang, lymne ka jingkñia ha kiwei pat ki blei, hynrei, tang ha U Trai.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ha kane kawei U Trai un map ïa la u shakri; haba u kynrad jong nga u leit sha ïing u Rimmon ban mane hangta, bad u shaniah ha ka kti jong nga, bad nga dem ïa lade ha ïing u Rimmon, haba nga dem ïa lade ha ïing u Rimmon, U Trai un map ïa u shakri jong me ha kane kaei kaei.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u la ong ha u, “To leit ha kaba suk.” Kumta, u la leit noh kham jngai khyndiat na u.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hynrei, u Gehasi, u shakri u Elisha uta u briew jong U Blei, u la ong, “Ha khmih; u kynrad jong nga u la pyllait ei ïa une u Naaman u nong Syria, um da shim ei ei na ki kti jong u ïa kata kaba u la wallam: katba im U Trai, ngan beh nadien jong u, bad ngan shim ei ei na u.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kumta, u Gehasi u la beh nadien u Naaman. Te haba u Naaman u la ïohi ba uwei u beh nadien jong u, u la hiar na ka kali ban leit tan ïa u, bad u la ong, “Kumno, ka bha?”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> U te u la ong, “Ka bha keiñ. U kynrad jong nga u la phah ïa nga u da ong, ‘Ha khmih, dang kumne la wan ha nga na ka ri lum Ephraim ar ngut ki samla na ki khun ki nongïathuhlypa; nga kyrpad ïa me, to ai ha ki, shi talent rupa bad ar riam ki jaiñ.’ ”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u Naaman u la ong, “To sngewbha, to shim ar talent.” Bad u la pynbor ïa u, bad u la song ïa kita ki ar talent rupa ha ki ar tylli ki pla, lem bad kita ki jaiñ ar riam, bad u la phah rah ïa ki ha ki shakri jong u ar ngut; bad ki la bah ïa ki ha shuwa jong u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te haba u la poi sha uta u lum, u la shim ïa ki na ki kti jong ki, bad u la buh ïa ki ha ïing; te haba u la pyllait ïa kita ki briew, ki la leit noh.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hynrei, u hi u la rung shapoh, bad u la ïeng ha khmat la u kynrad. Te u Elisha u la ong ha u, “Na-ei me wan, ko Gehasi?” U te u la ong, “U shakri jong me um shym leit shano shano.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te u la ong, “Hato ka dohnud jong nga kam shym leit lem bad me, mynba uta u briew u la phai pat na la ka kali ban tan ïa me? Hato ka long ka por ban shim sbai, bad ban shim ki jaiñkup, bad ki brisoh Olib bad ki brisoh Waiñ, bad ki langbrot bad ki masi, bad ki shakri shynrang bad ki shakri kynthei?",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Namar kata, ka pang 'ñiangthohlieh u Naaman kan bit ha me, bad ha u symbai jong me junom.” Bad u la leit mih noh na khmat jong u, u bapang 'ñiangthohlieh, lieh kat ka ïor."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki khun ki nongïathuhlypa ki la ong ha u Elisha, “Ha khmih te, kane ka jaka ba ngi shong ha khmat jong me ka khim eh ïa ngi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ngi kyrpad ïa me, to ngin ïaleit sha Jordan, bad ngin rah nangta mar uwei uwei u bim, bad ïa, ngin ïathaw jaka hangta, ha kaba ngi lah ban ïashong.” Te u la ong, “To leit.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te uwei u la ong, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to sngewbha ban leit lem bad la ki shakri.” U te u la ïathuh, “To ngan leit.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kumta, u la leit lem bad ki. Te ynda ki la ïapoi ha Jordan, ki la ïapom dieng.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hynrei, katba uwei u la dang khet ïa u bim, u sdie u la hap shapoh um; te u la pyrta, bad u la ong, “Waw, ko kynrad! namar uba la shu ïapan shibit.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u briew jong U Blei u la ong, “Ha-ei u la hap?” U te u la kdew ïa u ka jaka. Te haba u la pom u dieng, u la pashat ïa u shata, bad u la pynper ïa uta u nar.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U la ong te, “To shim ïa u sha me.” Kumta, u la kner ïa la ka kti, bad u la shim ïa u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u syiem ka Syria u la ïaleh thma bad ki Israel; bad u la ïasylla bad la ki shakri, u da ong, “Ha ka jaka kaba kum kata kan long ka dara jong nga.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u briew jong U Blei u la phah ktien ha u syiem ki Israel, u da ong, “To sumar ba men ym ïaid na kaba kum kata ka jaka; namar shata ki nong Syria ki la ïawan hiar.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u syiem ki Israel u la phah briew sha kata ka jaka kaba u briew U Blei u la ïathuh bad u la maham ïa u shaphang jong ka; bad u la pyllait im ïa lade hangta, ym tang shi sien ne ar sien.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ka dohnud u syiem ka Syria, ka la khuslai eh ïa kane; bad haba u la khot ïa la ki shakri, u la ong ha ki, “Phin ym ïathuh ïa nga uno na ngi uba ïashah ïa u syiem ki Israel?”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te uwei na ki shakri jong u, u la ong, “Em, ko syiem kynrad: hynrei, u Elisha uta u nongïathuhlypa ha Israel, u ïathuh ïa u syiem ki Israel ïa ki ktien kiba me kren ha la ka kamra thiah.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U te u la ong, “Khie leit khmih ha-ei u don, ba ngan phah wallam ïa u.” Te la ïathuh ïa u, da kaba ong, “Ha khmih, u don ha Dothan.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Namar kata, u la phah shata ki kulai bad ki kali ïapom, bad u paidïapom shibun: bad ki la leit poi mynmiet, bad ki la ker kut ïa ka shnong baroh sawdong.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te haba u shakri jong uta u briew jong U Blei u la khie dang step, bad u la mih noh, ha khmih, u paidïapom bad ki kulai bad ki kali ïapom ki la don baroh sawdong ka shnong. Bad u shakri jong u, u la ong ha u, “Waw, ko kynrad! Kumno ngin leh?”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U te u la ïathuh, “Wat sheptieng: naba kita kiba bad ngi ki long kham bun ban ïa kiba bad ki.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u Elisha u la duwai, bad u la ong, “A Trai, nga kyrpad ïa me, to pynpeit ïa ki khmat jong u, ba un ïohi.” Te U Trai u la pynpeit ïa ki khmat jong uta u samla; bad u la ïohi: te ha khmih, u lum u la dap da ki kulai bad ki kali ding baroh sawdong u Elisha.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te haba ki la hiar sha u, u Elisha u la duwai ha U Trai, bad u la ong, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to shoh ïa une u paid da ka jingmatlah.” Bad u la shoh ïa ki da ka jingmatlah kat kum ka ktien u Elisha.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te u Elisha u la ong ha ki, “Kane kam dei ka lynti, lymne kam dei kata ka shnong: to bud ïa nga, bad ngan ïalam ïa phi sha uta u briew uba phi ïawad.” Te u la ïalam ïa ki sha Samaria.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ynda ki la lah wan rung shapoh Samaria, u Elisha u la ong, “A Trai, pynpeit ïa ki khmat jong kine ki briew, ba kin ïohi.” Bad U Trai u la pynpeit ïa ki khmat jong ki, bad ki la ïohi; te ha khmih, ki la don hapdeng ka Samaria.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te u syiem ki Israel u la ong ha u Elisha, haba u la ïohi ïa ki, “Ko kpa, ngan pom ïa ki? Ngan pom ïa ki?”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> U te u la ïathuh, “Men ym pom ïa ki: men pom ne em ïa kita ïa kiba me la ring mraw da la ka waitlam bad da la ka ryntieh? to buh kpu bad um ha khmat jong ki, ba kin ïabam ïadih, bad ïaleit sha la u kynrad.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u la khreh jingbam ïa ki shibun eh: bad ynda ki la lah ïabam ïadih, u la pyllait noh ïa ki, te ki la leit noh sha la u kynrad. Kumta ki paidbah Syria kim shym ïawan shuh sha ka ri Israel.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te hadien kane, u Benhadad u syiem ka Syria u la ïalam lang ïa la u paidïapom baroh, bad haba u la leit kiew, u la ker kut ïa ka Samaria.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te la don ka 'nemsniew kaba jur ha Samaria, bad ha khmih, ki la ker kut ïa ka, haduh ba la die phraphew shekel rupa ïa ka khlieh kadda, bad shi pawa kab ka eit paro san shekel rupa.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te katba u syiem ki Israel u la dang ïaid nangta halor ka kynroh, kawei ka kynthei ka la pyrta ïa u, ka da ong, “Ïarap, ko syiem kynrad!”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> U te u la ong, “Lada U Trai um ïarap ïa pha, nangno ngan ïarap ïa pha? Na ki kynton, lane na ka jingtylliat umsoh?”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad u syiem u la ong ha ka, “Kaei kaba pynkhuslai ïa pha?” Ka te ka la ïathuh, “Kane ka briew ka la ong ïa nga, ‘To ai ïa u khun jong pha ba ngin ïoh bam ïa u mynta, bad ngin sa ïabam ïa u khun jong nga lashai.’",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kumta, ngi la ïashet ïa u khun jong nga, bad ngi la lah ïabam ïa u: bad nga la ong ïa ka, ha kaba kum lashai, ‘Ai sa u khun jong pha, ba ngin ïabam ïa u:’ ka te ka la buhrieh ïa la u khun.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te ynda u syiem u la ïohsngew ïa ki ktien kata ka kynthei, u la kad ïa la ki jaiñ; (te u la dang ïaid nangta halor ka kynroh;) bad ki briew ki la khmih, te ha khmih, u la don ka jaiñ byrni shapoh ha ka doh jong u.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ynda kumta, u la ong, “To U Blei un leh kumta ïa nga, bad kham tam ruh, lada ka khlieh u Elisha u khun u Shaphat kan neh ha u ha kane ka sngi.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Hynrei, u Elisha u la shong ha la ïing, bad ki tymmen basan ki ïashong lem bad u; te u syiem u la phah uwei u briew na khmat jong u: hynrei, shuwa ba um pat poi uta u nonglam-ktien ha u, u la ong ha ki tymmen basan, “Phi ïohi kumno une u khun u nongshohnoh u la phah ban shim noh ïa ka khlieh jong nga? to khmih, haba uta u briew u wan, to khang ïa ka jingkhang, bad bat skhem ïa ka jingkhang pyrshah ïa u: ym long ka jingsawa ki kjat u kynrad jong u hadien jong u?”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te katba u dang kren bad ki, ha khmih, uta u nonglam-ktien u la wan hiar ha u: u la ong te, “Ha khmih, kane ka basniew ka long na U Trai; balei ba ngan dang ap shuh ïa U Trai?”"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Elisha u la ong, “To sngew phi ïa ka ktien U Trai: ‘Kumne ong U Trai, Lashai kum ha kane ka por, shi shang u 'purew ni yn die shi shekel, bad ar shang u Barli shi shekel, ha ka khyrdop Samaria.’ ”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te uta u rangbah uba ha ka kti jong u, u syiem u shaniah u la ïathuh ha u briew jong U Blei, bad u la ong, “Ha khmih, lada U Trai un pynlong jingkhang ïit ha bneng, kane ka lah ban long?” U te u la ong, “Ha khmih, men ïohi da la ki khmat, hynrei, men ym ïoh bam ïa ka.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te la don saw ngut ki bapang 'thohlieh ha kaba rung sha ka khyrdop; bad ki la ïakren paralok, “Balei ngin ïashong hangne haduh ba ngin da ïap?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Lada ngin ong, ‘Ngin rung shapoh shnong,’ te ka 'nemsniew ka don ha ka shnong, bad ngin ïap hangta: bad lada ngin ïashong hangne, ngin ïap. Namar kata te, ïa ngin ïaleit hap sha u paidïapom ki Syria; lada kin pyllait im ïa ngi, te ngin im; bad lada kin pynïap ïa ngi ruh, tang ba ngin shu ïap.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kumta, ki la khie haba la kem ïongreiñ, ban leit sha ka dara ki Syria: bad haba ki la poi harud ka dara ki Syria, ha khmih, ym shym la don uwei u briew hangta.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Naba U Trai u la pynïohsngew ïa ki paidïapom ki Syria ïa ka jingsawa ki kali, bad ka jingsawa ki kulai, ka jingsawa u paidïapom uba shibun eh keiñ: bad ki la ïa-ong paralok hi, “Ha khmih, u syiem ki Israel u la ïawer ban ïaleh ïa ngi ïa ki syiem ki Hit, bad ïa ki syiem ki Ijipt, ban ïawan hiar thma sha ngi.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Namar kata, ki la khie bad ki la phet ïap la dang byrngut, bad ki la iehnoh ïa la ki ïingjaiñ, bad ïa la ki kulai, bad ïa la ki kadda, kata ka dara keiñ kumba ka la long, bad ki la phet ïap phet im.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te haba kine ki bapang 'ñiangthohlieh ki la poi harud kata ka dara, ki la leit rung sha kawei ka ïingjaiñ, bad ki la ïabam ïadih, bad ki la ïakit nangta ka rupa, bad ka ksiar, bad ki jaiñ, bad ki la leit buhrieh ïa ki; te ynda ki la phai pat, ki la leit rung sha kawei pat ka ïingjaiñ, bad ki la kit nangta ruh, bad ki la leit buhrieh ïa ka.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la ïa-ong paralok, “Ngim leh kaba dei: kane ka sngi ka long ka sngi ka khubor babha, bad ngi shu ïasngap: lada ngin ïa-ap haduh ban da shai mynstep, ka jingpynshitom kan lap ïa ngi: namar kata te, ïa ngin ïaleit ïathuh ha ïing u syiem.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kumta, haba ki la poi, ki la khot ïa ki nongap shnong: bad ki la ïathuh ïa ki, ki ïa-ong, “Ngi la leit poi sha ka dara ki Syria, te ha khmih, ym shym la don uwei u briew hangta, lymne ka jingsawa u briew, tang ki kulai ba la teh, bad ki kadda ba la teh, bad ki ïingjaiñ kumba ki la ju long.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ki la khot ïa ki nongap; ki ruh ki la ïathuh ha ka ïing u syiem hapoh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u syiem u la khie mynmiet, bad u la ong ha la ki shakri, “Ngan ïathuh ïa phi kaei ki Syria ki la leh ïa ngi. Ki tip ba ngi thngan; namar kata, ki la ïamih noh na kata ka dara ban buhrieh ïa lade sha lum, ki ïa-ong, ‘Ynda kin mih noh napoh ka shnong, ngin kem im ïa ki bad ngin ïoh leit rung shapoh ka shnong.’ ”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te uwei na ki shakri jong u, u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to kin shim san tylli na ki kulai kiba dang sah, ïa kiba la iehnoh ha ka shnong (ha khmih, ki long kum ki paidbah Israel baroh kiba la pynsah ha ka; ha khmih, ki long kum ki paidbah Israel baroh ïa kiba la bam duh:) bad to ngin ïaphah khmih.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ki la shim, namar kata, ar tylli ki kali bad ki kulai; bad u syiem u la phah bud nadien u paidïapom ki Syria, u da ong, “To ïaleit khmih.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ki la leit bud nadien jong ki haduh ka Jordan: te ha khmih, ka lynti baroh ka la dap da ki jaiñ bad ki khiew, kiba ki Syria ki la bred noh namar ka jingkyrkieh. Te ynda kita ki briew ba la phah ki la wan phai, ki la ïathuh ha u syiem.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u paidbah u la leit mih noh, bad u la lute ïa ka dara ki Syria. Kumta, shi shang u 'purew bani la die shi shekel, bad ar shang u Barli shi shekel, katba kum ka ktien U Trai.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u syiem u la thung ïa uta u rangbah uba ha ka kti jong u, u syiem u shaniah, ban sumar ïa ka khyrdop: te u paidbah u la ïuh ïa u ha kata ka khyrdop, bad u la ïap kumba u briew jong U Blei u la lah ong, uba la kren mynba u syiem u la wan hiar sha u.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te ka long kumta, kumba uta u briew jong U Blei u la lah kren ha u syiem, u da ong, “Ar shang u Barli shi shekel, bad shi shang u 'purew bani shi shekel, kan long lashai kum ha kane ka por ha ka khyrdop Samaria;”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bad uta u rangbah u la ïathuh ïa u briew jong U Blei, bad u la ong, “Te, ha khmih, lada U Trai un pynlong ki jingkhang ïit ha bneng, kat kane ka lah ban long?” U te u la ong, “Ha khmih, men ïohi ïa ka da la ki khmat, hynrei, men ym ïoh bam ïa ka:”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> kumta hi keiñ, ka la jia ha u; naba u paidbah u la ïuh ïa u ha kata ka khyrdop, bad u la ïap."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Elisha u la kren ha kata ka kynthei, kaba ïa u khun jong ka u la lah pynim pat, u da ong, “To ïeng, ma pha bad ka ïing jong pha, bad to leit shong kat shaba pha lah ban shong: naba U Trai u la hukum ban long 'nemsniew; bad kan long ruh halor ka ri, hynñiew snem.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te kata ka kynthei ka la ïeng, bad ka la leh kat kum ka ktien u briew jong U Blei: bad ka la leit lem bad la ka ïing, bad ka la shong ha ka ri ki Philistia hynñiew snem.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te ha ka bakut kita ki hynñiew snem, kata ka kynthei ka la wan phai pat na ka ri ki Philistia: bad ka la leit ïam ha u syiem ban ïoh ïa la ka ïing bad ïa la ka khyndew.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te u syiem u la dang ïakren bad u Gehasi, u shakri u briew jong U Blei, u da ong, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to ïathuh ïa nga ïa ki kam ki bakhraw baroh kiba u Elisha u la leh.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad katba u la dang ïathuh ïa u syiem kumno ba u la pynim pat ïa uta uba la ïap, te ha khmih, kata ka kynthei, kaba ïa u khun jong ka u la pynim, ka la ïam ha u syiem ban ïoh ïa la ka ïing bad ïa la ka khyndew. Bad u Gehasi u la ong, “Ko syiem kynrad, kane ka long kata ka kynthei, bad une u long u khun jong ka, ïa uba u Elisha u la pynim pat.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te haba u syiem u la kylli ïa kata ka kynthei, ka la ïathuh ha u. Kumta, u syiem u la buh na ka bynta jong ka uwei u rangbah, u da ong, “To pynai pat baroh kaba dei ka jong ka, bad ki jingmih ka lyngkha baroh naduh kata ka sngi ba ka la iehnoh ïa la ka ri, haduh mynta keiñ.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u Elisha u la leit poi sha Damaskos; bad u Benhadad u syiem ka Syria u la pang; bad ki la ïathuh ha u, ki ïa-ong, “Uta u briew jong U Blei u la wan poi shane.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U syiem te u la ong ha u Hasael, “To rah ka jingai sngewbha ha la ka kti, bad to leit ïashem ïa u briew jong U Blei, bad to ïakylli ïa U Trai da u, da kaba ong, ‘Ngan koit pat ne em na kane ka jingpang?’ ”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kumta u Hasael u la leit ïashem bad u, bad u la rah ha la ka kti ïa ka jingai sngewbha, na ki kynja babha jong ka Damaskos baroh keiñ, sawphew kit ki ut, bad haba u la wan u la ïeng ha khmat jong u, bad u la ong ruh, “U khun jong me u Benhadad u syiem ka Syria u la phah ïa nga ha me, u da ong, ‘Ngan koit pat ne em na kane ka jingpang?’ ”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U Elisha te u la ong ha u, “Khie leit, ong ïa u, ‘Men koit pat da shisha’; pynban, U Trai u la pyni ha nga ba un ïap da shisha.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u la khmih shaiñ ha u, haduh ba u la lehrain: bad uta u briew jong U Blei u la ïam.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u Hasael u la ong, “Balei ba u kynrad jong nga u ïam?” U te u la ïathuh, “Namar nga tip ïa ka basniew kaba men leh ha ki khun Israel: ïa ki kut baskhem jong ki men wiang da ka ding, ïa ki samla jong ki men pynïap da ka waitlam, bad men lympat lyngkhot lyngkhai ïa ki khunlung jong ki, bad men tar ïa ki kynthei jong ki, kiba punkhun.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U Hasael te u la ong, “U shakri jong me u long uei, uba long tang u ksew, ba un leh ïa ka bakhraw kat kane?” Bad u Elisha u la ïathuh, “U Trai u la pyni ha nga ba men long syiem halor ka Syria.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ynda kumta, u la leit noh na u Elisha, bad u la wan sha la u kynrad; uba la ong ha u, “U Elisha u la ong aïu ïa me?” U te u la ïathuh u la ong ha nga “ba men koit pat da shisha.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te kum lashai, u la shim ka jaiñkup thiah, bad u la wieh ïa ka ha ka um, u la tap ïa ka ha ka khmat jong u, kumta, u la ïap: bad u Hasael u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te ha ka snem ka basan jong u Joram u khun u Ahab u syiem ki Israel, u Jehoshaphat u long mynkata u syiem ha Judah, u Jehoram u khun u Jehoshaphat u syiem ka Judah u la sdang ban synshar.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U la long laiphew ar snem ka rta mynba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar phra snem ha Jerusalem.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u la ïaid ha ka lynti ki syiem ki Israel, kumba la leh ka ïing u Ahab: naba u la shongkurim ïa ka khun u Ahab: bad u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> La kumta ruh, U Trai un ym pynduh ïa ka Judah, na ka bynta u Dabid u shakri jong u, kumba u la kular ha u ban ai ha u ka sharak, bad ha ki khun jong u borabor.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ha ki sngi jong u, ka Edom ka la ïaleh bad ka la lait na ka kti ki Judah, bad ka la thung la u jong hi u syiem.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ynda kumta, u Joram u la leit sha Sair, bad ki kali ïapom jong u baroh lem bad u: bad haba u la khie joit mynmiet, u la pom ïa ki Edom kiba ker tawiar ïa u, bad ïa ki kaptan ki kali: bad u paidbah u la phet ïap sha la ki ïingjaiñ.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kumta ka Edom ka la ïaleh bad ka la lait na ka kti ka Judah, haduh kane ka sngi. Ynda kumta, ka Libnah ruh ka la ïaleh bad ka la lait ha kajuh ka por.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Joram, bad baroh kaba u la leh, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ka Judah?",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u Joram u la thiah bad la ki kpa, bad la tep ïa u lem bad la ki kpa ha ka shnong u Dabid: bad u Ahasaïah u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ha ka snem ka bakhat-ar jong u Joram u khun u Ahab u syiem ki Israel, u Ahasaïah u khun u Jehoram u syiem ka Judah u la sdang ban synshar.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> U Ahasaïah u la long arphew ar snem ka rta mynba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar shi snem ha Jerusalem. Bad ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka la long “ka Athaliah” ka khun u Omri u syiem ki Israel.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad u la ïaid ha ka lynti ka ïing u Ahab, bad u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai, kumba la leh ka ïing u Ahab: naba u la long u pyrsa kurim ka ïing u Ahab.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te u la leit lem bad u Joram u khun u Ahab ban ïaleh thma ïa u Hasael u syiem ka Syria ha Ramoth-gilead: bad ki Syria ki la pynmong ïa u Joram.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad u syiem Joram u la wan phai pat sha Jesril ban ïoh pynkhiah ïa u na kita ki jingmong kiba ki Syria ki la lah pynmong ïa u ha Ramah, mynba u la ïaleh ïa u Hasael u syiem ka Syria. Te u Ahasaïah u khun u Jehoram u syiem ka Judah u la leit hiar sha Jesril ban leit khmih ïa u Joram u khun u Ahab, namar ba u la pang."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Elisha u nongïathuhlypa, ynda u la khot ïa uwei na ki khun ki nongïathuhlypa, u la ong ïa u, “To panpoh ïa la ka syngkai, bad to shim ïa une u khiew umphniang ha la ka kti, bad khie leit sha Ramoth-gilead.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ynda me la poi shata, wad hangta ïa u Jehu u khun u Jehoshaphat u khun u Nimshi, bad to leit shapoh, bad to pynïeng ïa u napdeng ki para jong u, bad leit lam ïa u sha ka kamra kaba kham shapoh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ynda kumta, to shim ïa uta u khiew umphniang, bad theh ïa ka ha ka khlieh jong u, bad to ong ruh, ‘Kumne ong U Trai, “Nga la pynsleh ïa me ban long syiem halor ki Israel.” ’ Te haba me la plie ïa ka jingkhang, to phet ïap, bad wat sangeh shuh.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kumta, uta u samla, uta u nongïathuhlypa ba samla keiñ, u la leit sha Ramoth-gilead.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ynda u la poi, ha khmih, ki kaptan u paidïapom ki dang ïashong; te u la ong, “Nga don ka khubor ha me, ko kaptan.” U Jehu te u la ong, “Ha uno na ngi baroh?” U te u la ong, “Ha me keiñ, ko kaptan.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u la ïeng joit, bad u la leit shapoh ïing; bad u la theh ïa kata ka umphniang halor ka khlieh jong u, bad u la ong ha u, “Kumne ong U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, ‘Nga la pynsleh ïa me ban long syiem halor u paidbah jong U Trai, halor ki Israel keiñ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te men shoh ïa ka ïing u Ahab u kynrad jong me, ba ngan ïoh pynhiar kput ïa ka snam ki shakri jong nga ki nongïathuhlypa, bad ïa ka snam ki shakri jong U Trai baroh, ha ka kti ka Jesebel.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Naba ka ïing u Ahab baroh kan duh noh khoit: bad ngan ot noh na u Ahab ïa u shynrang briew baroh, bad ïa uta uba la set kut, bad ïa uta uba sah laitluid ha Israel.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad ngan pynlong ïa ka ïing u Ahab kum ïa ka ïing u Jeroboam u khun u Nebat, bad kum ka ïing u Baasha u khun u Ahijah.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ki ksew kin bam ïa ka Jesebel ha ka bynta ka Jesril, bad yn ym don ba tep ïa ka.’ ” Te haba u la plie ïa ka jingkhang, u la phet ïap.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ynda kumta, u Jehu u la mih noh sha ki shakri u kynrad jong u: bad uwei u la ong ha u, “Kumno, ka bha? balei ba une u briew balamwir u wan ha me?” Te u la ong ha ki, “Phi ithuh ïa uta u briew bad shaphang aïu ba u kren.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ki la ong, “Kata kaba lamler; to ïathuh ha ngi mynta.” U te u la ong, “Kumne u la kren ha nga, u ong, ‘Kumne ong U Trai, Nga la pynsleh ïa me ban long syiem halor ki Israel.’ ”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hangta ki la pynkloi, bad ki la shim uwei uwei baroh ïa la ka jaiñkup, bad ki la buh ïa ka hapoh jong u halor khlieh ki kyrdan, bad ki la put ka turoi, ki ïa-ong, “U Jehu u long syiem.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te kumta, u Jehu u khun u Jehoshaphat u khun u Nimshi u la ïashet pyrshah ïa u Joram. (Te u Joram u la dang ïa-ap ïa ka Ramoth-gilead, ma u bad ki Israel baroh, namar u Hasael u syiem ka Syria.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hynrei, u syiem Joram u la leit phai sha Jesril ban ïoh khiah na kita ki jingmong kiba ki Syria ki la lah pynmong ïa u, mynba u la ïaleh thma bad u Hasael u syiem ka Syria.) Te u Jehu u la ong, “Lada kane ka long ka jingmut jong phi, wat shah ban lait uwei ban mih na ka shnong, ban leit ïathuh ha Jesril.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kumta, u Jehu u la shong kali, bad u la leit sha Jesril; naba u Joram u sah hangta. Bad u Ahasaïah u syiem ka Judah u la leit hiar ban khmih ïa u Joram.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u nongap u la ïeng halor ka kut ha Jesril, bad u la ïohi ïa ka kynhun u Jehu katba u la nang wan, bad u la ong, “Nga ïohi kawei ka kynhun.” Te u Joram u la ong, “Khreh nongshong kulai, bad to phah tan ïa ki, bad to un ong, ‘Ka jingsuk ne em?’ ”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Kumta, la leit uwei halor u kulai ban leit tan ïa u, bad u la ong, “Kumne ong u syiem, ‘Ka jingsuk ne em?’ ” Bad u Jehu u la ong, “Me donkam aïu bad ka jingsuk? To phai me shadien jong nga.” Te uta u nongap u la ïathuh, u da ong, “Uta u nonglam-ktien u la poi sha ki, hynrei, um wan phai pat.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ynda kumta, u la phah sa ïa u ba-ar halor kulai, uba, ynda u la poi sha ki, u la ong, “Kumne ong u syiem, ‘Ka jingsuk ne em?’ ” Te u Jehu u la ïathuh, “Me donkam aïu bad ka jingsuk? To phai me shadien jong nga.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te uta u nongap u la ïathuh, u da ong, “U la poi haduh sha ki, hynrei, um wan phai pat: bad ka jingpynmareh kali ka long kum ka jingpynmareh u Jehu u khun u Nimshi; naba u pynmareh i runar eh.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u Joram u la ong, “Khreh ka kali.” Bad ki la khreh ïa ka kali jong u. Te u Joram u syiem ki Israel bad u Ahasaïah u syiem ka Judah ki la ïaleit mih noh mar ha la ka kali, bad ki la leit tan ïa u Jehu, bad ki la shem ïa u ha ka bynta jong u Naboth u nong Jesril,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te ynda u Joram u la ïohi ïa u Jehu, u la ong, “Ka jingsuk ne em, ko Jehu?” U te u la ïathuh, “Ka jingsuk aïu, katba ki jingleh nuti ka kmie jong me ka Jesebel bad ki jingkren byrtong jong ka ki bun eh katta katta?”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u Joram u la pynphai ïa la ki kti, bad u la phet ïap, bad u la ong ha u Ahasaïah, “Ka jingshetkylla, ko Ahasaïah.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te u Jehu u la wiat ïa la ka ryntieh katba lah ka bor jong u, bad u la dei ïa u Joram napdeng ki siang tyrpeng jong u, bad u khnam u la pei ha u dohnud jong u, te u la kyllon ha la ka kali ïapom.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te u Jehu u la ong ha u Bidkar u kaptan jong u, “To rah, to bred ruh ïa u ha ka bynta ka lyngkha u Naboth u nong Jesril: naba to kynmaw kumno, mynba nga bad me ngi la ïashong kulai lem hadien u Ahab u kpa jong u, ba U Trai u la buh kane ka jingkit halor jong u.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> ‘Shisha nga la ïohi mynhynnin ïa ka snam u Naboth, bad ïa ka snam ki khun jong u,’ ong U Trai; ‘bad ngan siew kylliang ïa me ha kane ka jaka,’ ong U Trai. Namar kata te to rah to bred ruh ïa u ha kata ka bynta ka khyndew, katba kum ka ktien U Trai.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Hynrei, naba u Ahasaïah u syiem ka Judah u la ïohi ïa kane, u la phet ïap na ka lynti ka ïingkper. Bad u Jehu u la bud nadien jong u, bad u la ong, “Pynïap ïa u ruh ha ka kali:” bad ki la pom ïa u hamar u thiep Gur, kaba hajan Ibleam. Te haba u la phet ïap sha Megiddo, u la ïap hangta.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad ki shakri jong u ki la pynkit ïa u ha ka kali ïapom sha Jerusalem, bad ki la tep ïa u ha ka jingtep jong u lem bad la ki kpa ha ka shnong u Dabid.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te ha ka snem khatwei jong u Joram u khun u Ahab, u Ahasaïah u la sdang ban synshar ha Judah.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te ynda u Jehu u la wan poi sha Jesril, ka Jesebel ka la bna ïa kata; te ynda ka la kyllan rong ïa la ka khmat, bad ka la pynitynnad ïa la ka khlieh, ka la khmih shabar na ka jingkhang ïit.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te katba u Jehu u la rung ha ka khyrdop, ka la ong, “Ka jingsuk ne em, me u Simri, u nongshohnoh kynrad?”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad u la khmied ïa la ka khmat sha ka jingkhang ïit, bad u la ong, “Mano ba don ha ka liang jong nga? mano?” Bad ar ngut ne lai ngut ki ïunukh ki la peit sha u.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te u la ong, “To pynnoh ïa ka.” Kumta, ki la pynnoh ïa ka: te don na ka snam jong ka ba la bit ïa ka kynroh, bad ïa ki kulai: bad u la ïuh ïa ka hapoh ki kjat.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te ynda u la rung shapoh; u la bam u la dih; bad u la ong, “To leit, khmih mynta ïa kane ka briew ba la tim, bad to tep ïa ka: naba ka long ka khun u syiem.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Te ki la ïaleit ban tep ïa ka: hynrei, kim shym la shem ei ei nalor ka shynrong khlieh, bad ki kjat, bad ki sla'ti jong ka.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Namar kata, ki la wan pat, bad ki la ïathuh ha u. Te u la ong, “Kane ka long ka ktien U Trai, kaba u la kren da u shakri jong u, u Elijah u nong Tishbi, u da ong, ‘Ha ka bynta ka Jesril ki ksew kin bam ïa ka doh ka Jesebel:",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> bad ka metïap ka Jesebel kan long kum ka kynsha halor ka lyngkha ha ka bynta ka Jesril; kumta kin ym ïa-ong, “Kane ka Jesebel.” ’ ”"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Ahab u la don hynñiewphew ngut ki khun shynrang ha Samaria. Bad u Jehu u la thoh ki shithi, bad u la phah sha Samaria, ha ki nongsynshar ka Jesril, ha ki tymmen basan keiñ, bad ha kita kiba la sumar ïa ki khun u Ahab, u da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Mynta te tang shu poi kane ka shithi ha phi, namar ba ki khun u kynrad jong phi ki don bad phi, bad don bad phi ki kali bad ki kulai, bad ka shnong ba la ker kynroh ruh, bad ki atiar;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> to khmih ïa u babha tam bad ïa uba bit tam na ki khun u kynrad jong phi, bad to pynshong ïa u halor ka khet u kpa jong u, bad to ïaleh na ka bynta ka ïing u kynrad jong phi.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, ki la sheptieng shikatdei eh, bad ki la ong, “Ha khmih, kita ar ngut ki syiem kim shym la ïeng ha khmat jong u: kumno te ngi ngin ïeng?”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te uta uba halor ka ïing, bad uta uba halor ka shnong, ki tymmen basan ruh, bad kita kiba la sumar ïa ki khynnah, ki la phah ktien ha u Jehu, ki ïa-ong, “Ngi long ki shakri jong me, ngin leh baroh kat kaba men hukum ïa ngi; ngin ym thung syiem da uno uno ruh: to leh ma me ïa kaba me ibit ha khmat jong me.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ynda kumta, u la thoh shithi sha ki ka ba-ar sien, u da ong, “Lada phi long ha ka liang jong nga bad lada phin sngap ïa ka ktien jong nga, to wan rah ïa ki khlieh kita ki briew ki khun u kynrad jong phi, sha nga ha Jesril hamar kane ka por lashai.” Te kita ki khun u syiem, kiba long hynñiewphew ngut, ki la don bad ki bakhraw batri jong ka shnong, kiba ju sumar ïa ki.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te haba kata ka shithi ka la poi sha ki, ki la shim ïa kita ki khun u syiem, bad ki la pynïap ïa ki, hynñiewphew ngut keiñ, bad ki la buh ïa ki khlieh jong ki ha ki shang, bad ki la phah ïa ki sha u ha Jesril.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te la wan poi u nonglam-ktien, uba la ïathuh ha u, u da ong, “Ki la wallam ïa kita ki khlieh ki khun u syiem.” U te u la ong, “Buh ïa ki ar kynton ha kaba rung sha ka khyrdop haduh mynstep.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ha kaba mynstep, u la leit mih shabar, bad haba u la ïeng, u la ong ha ki briew baroh, “Phi long ki bahok: ha khmih, nga, nga la ïashet ïa la u kynrad, bad nga la pynïap ïa u: hynrei, mano ba la pynïap ïa kine baroh?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> To tip mynta ba ym don ei ei ka ban hap ha ka khyndew na ka ktien U Trai, kaba U Trai u la kren shaphang ka ïing u Ahab: naba U Trai u la leh ïa kata kaba u la kren da la u shakri u Elijah.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kumta, u Jehu u la pynïap ïa kiba dang sah baroh na ka ïing u Ahab ha Jesril, bad ki rangbah jong u baroh, bad ki lok ba-ieit jong u, bad ïa ki lyngdoh jong u, haduh ba um pynsah shuh uwei ruh ïa u.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te haba u la ïeng u la leit noh, bad u la leit poi sha Samaria. Bad katba u don ha ka ïing ot shñiuh jong ki nongaplangbrot ha lynti,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> u Jehu u la ïakynduh bad ki para u Ahasaïah u syiem ka Judah, bad u la ong, “Phi long kiei?” Te ki la ïathuh, “Ngi long ki para u Ahasaïah: bad ngi ïaleit hiar ban khublei ïa ki khun u syiem bad ïa ki khun ka syiem.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U te u la ong, “To kem im ïa ki.” Bad ki la kem im ïa ki, bad ki la pynïap ïa ki ha ka thliew ka ïing ot shñiuh, sawphew ar ngut keiñ; lymne um shym pynsah uwei na ki.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te haba u la leit mih noh nangta, u la ïakynduh ïa u Jehonadab u khun u Rekhab uba wan tan ïa u: bad u la khublei ïa u, bad u la ong ha u, “Ka dohnud jong me ka beit, kumba ka dohnud jong nga ka long bad ka jong me?” U Jehonadab te u la ïathuh, “Ka long keiñ.” “Lada ka long, to ai ha nga ïa ka kti jong me.” Bad u la ai ha u ïa la ka kti; bad u pynkiew ïa u ha u ha ka kali ïapom.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u la ong, “To wan bad nga, bad to khmih ïa ka jingshitrhem jong nga na ka bynta U Trai.” Kumta, ki la pynshong ïa u ha ka kali jong u.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te ynda u la poi sha Samaria, u la pynïap baroh kiba dang sah ki jong u Ahab ha Samaria, haduh ba u la lah pynduh khoit ïa u, kat kum ka ktien U Trai, kaba u la kren ha u Elijah.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u Jehu u la ïalum lang ïa ki briew baroh, bad u la ong ha ki, “U Ahab u la shakri ïa u Baal khyndiat; hynrei, u Jehu un shakri ïa u shibun.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Namar kata te, to khot ha nga ïa ki nongïathuhlypa u Baal baroh, ïa ki nongmane jong u baroh, bad ïa ki lyngdoh jong u baroh; wat ai ban jah uwei: naba nga don ka jingkñia ka bakhraw ïa u Baal; jar uba jah, un ym im.” Hynrei, u Jehu u la leh ïa ka da ka buit sianti, khnang ba un ïoh pynduh noh khoit ïa ki nongmane u Baal.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Jehu u la ong, “To pynkyntang ïa ka jingïaseng bakhuid ïa u Baal.” Bad ki la pynbna ïa ka.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u Jehu u la phah ha ki Israel baroh: bad ki nongmane u Baal baroh ki la ïawan, ba ym don uwei u briew uba sah khlem wan. Bad ki la ïawan ha ka ïing u Baal; bad ka ïing u Baal ka la dap nadong shadong.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u la ong ha uta u briew uba ju sumar ïa ka kamra ki jaiñ lyngdoh, “To sei ïa ki jaiñ ïa ki nongmane u Baal baroh.” Te u la wallam ïa kita ki jaiñ ïa ki.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> U Jehu te bad u Jehonadab u khun u Rekhab ki la leit shapoh ka ïing u Baal; bad u la ong ha ki nongmane u Baal, “To ïit, to khmih ruh, ba ym don hangne bad phi uwei ruh na ki shakri U Trai, hynrei, tang ki nongmane u Baal hi.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te ki la rung shapoh ban ai ïa ki jingkñia bad ïa ki jingainguh thang. Te u Jehu u la buh ha u, phraphew ngut ki rangbah shabar, bad u la ong, “Lada uwei na kine ki briew kiba nga la wallam ha ki kti jong phi un lait, uta uba pyllait ïa u, ka jingim jong u kan long na ka bynta ka jingim jong uta.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te u tang shu la lah ai ïa ka jingainguh thang, u Jehu u la ong ha kita ki nongap bad ha ki kaptan, “To rung, bad pynïap ïa ki; wat shah ba uwei ruh un mih.” Bad ki la pynïap ïa ki da ka syrti waitlam; bad ki nongap bad ki kaptan ki la bred ïa ki shabar, bad ki la leit sha ka shnong ka ïing u Baal.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad ki la sei noh ïa ki durblei kiba la don ha ka ïing u Baal, bad ki la thang ïa ki.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad ki la pynkyllon ïa ka dur u Baal, bad ki la pyntwa ïa ka ïing u Baal, bad ki la pynlong ïa ka, ka ïing thehñiut, haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kumne u Jehu u la pynduh noh ïa u Baal na Israel.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Hynrei, na ki pop u Jeroboam u khun u Nebat, da kiba u la pynleh pop ïa ki Israel, u Jehu um shym kynriah noh na kaba bud ïa ki, kita ki khun masi ksiar keiñ kiba la don ha Bethel, bad kiba la don ha Dan.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Jehu, “Namar ba me la leh bha ha kaba leh ïa kata kaba dei ha khmat jong nga, bad me la leh ïa ka ïing u Ahab kat kum kata baroh kaba la don ha ka dohnud jong nga, ki khun jong me haduh ka basaw pateng kin shong halor ka khet ki Israel.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Hynrei, u Jehu um shym sumar ban ïaid ha ka hukum U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, da ka dohnud jong u baroh: um shym kynriah noh na ki pop u Jeroboam, da kiba u la pynleh pop ïa ki Israel.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ha kita ki sngi, U Trai u la sdang ban pynrit ïa ki Israel: bad u Hasael u la pom ïa ki ha ki phang ki Israel baroh;",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> na Jordan shaphang mihngi, ka ri Gilead baroh, ki Gad, bad ki Reuben, bad ki Manasseh, naduh Aroer, kaba ha khap ka them Arnon, ïa ka Gilead bad ïa ka Bashan keiñ.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Jehu, bad kaba u la leh baroh, bad ka bor jong u baroh, ym shym thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ki Israel?",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Te u Jehu u la thiah noh bad la ki kpa: bad ki la tep ïa u ha Samaria. Bad u Jehoahas u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te ka por ba u Jehu u la synshar halor ki Israel ha Samaria ka la long arphew phra snem."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ynda ka Athaliah ka kmie u Ahasaïah ka la ïohi ba u khun jong ka u la ïap, ka la ïeng joit bad ka la pynduh ïa ka jaid syiem baroh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Hynrei ka Jehosheba, ka khun u syiem Joram, ka para u Ahasaïah, ka la shim ïa u Joash u khun u Ahasaïah, bad ka la rah noh ïa u napdeng ki khun u syiem ïa kiba la pynïap, ma u keiñ bad ka aïa jong u, bad la buh ïa ki ha kamra thiah; bad ki la buhrieh ïa u na ka Athaliah, kumta, ym shym la pynïap ïa u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad la buhrieh ïa u lem bad ka ha ka ïing U Trai hynriew snem: bad ka Athaliah ka la synshar halor ka ri.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ha ka snem ka bahynñiew, u Jehoïada u la phah wallam ïa ki kaptan ki shispah na ki Karit bad na ki nongap, bad u la wallam ïa ki ha u sha ïing U Trai; bad u la pynlong jutang bad ki, bad u la pynsmai ïa ki ha ka ïing U Trai, bad u la pyni ha ki, ïa u khun u syiem.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u la hukum ïa ki, u da ong, “Ïa kane phi dei ban leh: shi bynta na ka balai jong phi, kiba wan rung ha ka Sabbaton, kin long ki nongap ïa ka ïing u syiem;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad shi bynta kin long ha ka khyrdop Sur; bad shi bynta hajan ka khyrdop shadien ki nongap: kumta, phin ap ïa kata ka ïing, bad phin long ka jingker.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ar kynhun na phi, baroh keiñ kiba mih noh ha ka Sabbaton, kin ap ïa ka ïing U Trai baroh sawdong ïa u syiem.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad phin ïeng tawiar ïa u syiem, u briew baroh bad la ka atiar ha la ka kti: bad ïa uta uba wan rung shapoh ki jingker, to pynïap ïa u: bad phin long lem bad u syiem haba u mih shabar, bad haba u wan shapoh.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad ki kaptan ki shispah ki la leh katba kum kata baroh kaba u Jehoïada lyngdoh u la hukum: bad uwei uwei baroh u la shim ïa la ki briew, kita kiba dei ban wan rung ha ka Sabbaton, lem bad kita kiba dei ban mih noh ha ka Sabbaton, bad ki la ïawan ha u Jehoïada lyngdoh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Uta u lyngdoh te u la aiti ha ki kaptan ki shispah ïa ki sum bad ki stieh kiba la ju long ki jong u syiem Dabid, kiba la don ha kata ka ïing U Trai.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kumta, ki nongap ki la ïeng hajan u syiem baroh sawdong, u briew baroh bad la ki atiar ha la ka kti, naduh ka krung kamon jong ka ïing haduh ka krung kadiang jong ka ïing, baroh shilynter ka duwan bad ka ïing.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ynda kumta, u la pynmih noh ïa uta u khun u syiem, bad u la pynphong ïa u ka pansngiat, bad u la ai ka jingphla ha u; te haba ki la thung syiem ïa u, ki la pynsleh ïa u; bad ki la ïathab kti, bad ki la ïa-ong, “U Blei un pynim ïa u syiem.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ynda ka Athaliah ka la ïohsngew ïa ka jingrisa ki nongap bad jong u paidbah, ka la wan mih ha u paidbah ha ka ïing U Trai:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad ka la khmih, te ha khmih, u syiem u ïeng hajan u rishot, kumba ju don ka rukom, bad ki kaptan bad ki turoi hajan u syiem; bad u paidbah ka ri baroh u la ïalehkmen, bad ki la put turoi. Ynda kumta, ka Athaliah ka la kad ïa la ki jaiñ, bad ka la pyrta, “Ka jingshetkylla, ka jingshetkylla!”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u Jehoïada lyngdoh u la hukum ïa ki kaptan ki shispah ïa kiba la thung halor u paidïapom, bad u la ong ha ki, “Pynmih noh ïa ka napdeng ki jingker; bad ïa uta uba bud ïa ka to pynïap da ka waitlam:” naba u lyngdoh u la ong, “Wat ai ban pynïap ïa ka ha ka ïing U Trai!”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kumta, ki la pyllait jaka ïa ka bad ka la mih na ka lynti ba ju rung ki kulai sha ïing u syiem: bad hangta la pynïap ïa ka.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u Jehoïada u la pynlong jutang hapdeng U Trai bad u syiem bad u paidbah, ba kin long u paidbah jong U Trai; hapdeng u syiem bad u paidbah ruh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u paidbah baroh jong ka ri u la leit sha ïing u Baal, bad ki la pynkyllon ïa ka; ïa ki duwan bad ïa ki dur jong u ki la lympat lyngkhot lyngkhai baroh phar, bad ki la pynïap ïa u Mattan u lyngdoh u Baal ha khmat ki duwan. Te u lyngdoh u la thung ki rangbah ha ka ïing U Trai.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u la shim ïa ki kaptan ki shispah, bad ïa ki Karit, bad ïa ki nongap, bad ïa ki briew jong ka ri baroh; bad ki la wallam arsut ïa u syiem na ka ïing U Trai, bad ki la wan na ka lynti ka khyrdop ki nongap sha ka ïing u syiem. Bad u la shong ruh halor ka khet ki syiem.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kumta, ki briew ka ri baroh ki la ïakmen, bad ka shnong ka la suk: bad ki la pynïap ïa ka Athaliah da ka waitlam hajan ka ïing u syiem.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U Jehoash u la long hynñiew snem ka rta mynba u la sdang ban synshar."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ha ka snem ka bahynñiew u Jehu, u Jehoash u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar sawphew snem ha Jerusalem: bad ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka la long “ka Sibiah” kaba na Beer-sheba.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u Jehoash u la leh kata kaba dei ha khmat U Trai ki sngi jong u baroh ha kiba u Jehoïada lyngdoh u la hikai ïa u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> La kumta ruh, ïa ki jaka bajrong ym shym la pynduh noh: ki briew ki la dang kñia bad ki thang ki jingiwbih ha ki jaka bajrong.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te u Jehoash u la ong ha ki lyngdoh, “U sbai baroh jong kiei kiei ba la kyntang ïa uba la wallam sha ka ïing U Trai, u sbai ba ju siew, u sbai ka jingkheiñ dor ki briew uwei pa uwei, bad ïa u sbai baroh ba-mih ha ka dohnud u briew ban wallam ha ka ïing U Trai,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> to ki lyngdoh kin shim ïa u ha ki, u briew baroh na la u lok: bad kin shna pat ïa ki jingpra jong ka ïing, kat kaba yn shem ïa kano kano ka jingpra.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ha ka ba-arphew lai snem u syiem Jehoash, ki lyngdoh kim pat shna pat ïa ki jingpra jong ka ïing.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem Jehoash u la khot ïa u Jehoïada lyngdoh, bad ïa kiwei pat de ki lyngdoh, bad u la ong ha ki, “Balei phim shna pat ïa ki jingpra jong ka ïing? namar kata te, wat shim sbai shuh na la ki lok, hynrei, to aiti ïa u na ka bynta ki jingpra jong ka ïing.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ki lyngdoh te ki la ïakohnguh ban ym shim sbai shuh na u paidbah, lymne shna pat ïa ki jingpra jong ka ïing.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hynrei, u Jehoïada lyngdoh u la shim kawei ka synduk, bad u la sam thliew ha ka jingtap jong ka, bad u la buh ïa ka hajan ka duwan, shaphang kamon haba rung sha ka ïing U Trai: bad ki lyngdoh kiba ap ïa ka jingkhang ki la thep ha ka, ïa u sbai baroh ba la wallam sha ïing U Trai.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ynda ki la ïohi ba don shibun u sbai ha kata ka synduk, u nongthoh u syiem bad u rangbah lyngdoh ki la leit kiew, bad ki la thep ha ki byrni bad ki la kheiñ ïa uta u sbai ba la shem ha ka ïing U Trai.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ki la ai ïa uta u sbai ba la thew ha ki kti jong kita kiba la trei ïa kata ka kam, kiba la sumar ïa ka ïing U Trai: bad ki la siew ïa u ha ki misteri bad ha ki nongtei kynroh, kiba la trei ha ka ïing U Trai,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> bad ha ki nongtrei kynroh bad kiba shtah maw, bad ïa ka ban thied dieng bad mawshtah ban shna pat ïa ka jingpra ka ïing U Trai, bad ïa kaba lut baroh na ka bynta ka ïing ban shna pat ïa ka.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, ïa ka ïing U Trai ym shym la thaw ki khuri rupa, ki jinglur sharak, ki khiew, ki turoi, kino kino ki pliang ksiar, lane ki pliang rupa, da uta u sbai ïa uba la wallam sha ïing U Trai:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> naba ki la ai ïa uta ha kita kiba la trei ïa ka kam, bad ki la shna pat da u ïa ka ïing U Trai.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Lymne kim shym ïakheiñ bad kita ki briew, ha kiba ki la aiti ïa uta u sbai ban ai ha kita kiba la trei ïa ka kam: naba ki la leh hok.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ïa u sbai namar ki jingainguh jingrem, bad ïa u sbai namar ki jingainguh pop, ym shym la wallam shapoh ka ïing U Trai: uta u la long u jong ki lyngdoh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ynda kumta, u Hasael u syiem ka Syria u la leit kiew, bad u la ïaleh thma ïa ka Gath bad u la jop ïa ka: bad u Hasael u la thew ïa la ka khmat ban leit kiew sha Jerusalem.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u Jehoash u syiem ka Judah u la shim ïa kiei kiei ba la kyntang baroh kiba u Jehoshaphat, bad u Jehoram, bad u Ahasaïah, ki kpa jong u, ki syiem ka Judah, ki la lah pynkyntang, bad kiei kiei ba la kyntang ki jong u hi, bad ïa ka ksiar baroh ba la shem ha ki jingkynshew ka ïing U Trai, bad ha ïing u syiem, bad u la phah ïa ki ha u Hasael u syiem ka Syria: u te u la leit noh na Jerusalem.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Joash, bad baroh kaba u la leh, ym shym thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ka Judah?",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ki shakri jong u ki la ïeng joit, bad haba ki la ïashet, ki la pom ïa u Joash ha ka ïing Millo, ha ka lynti baleit hiar sha Silla.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Naba u Josakar u khun u Shimeath, bad u Jehosabad u khun u Shomer, ki shakri jong u, ki la pynïap ïa u, bad u la ïap; bad ki la tep ïa u bad la ki kpa ha ka shnong u Dabid: bad u Amasaïah u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ha ka snem ka ba-arphew lai u Joash u khun u Ahasaïah, u syiem ka Judah, u Jehoahas u khun u Jehu u la sdang ban synshar halor ki Israel ha Samaria, bad u la synshar khathynñiew snem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai, bad u la bud ïa ki pop u Jeroboam u khun u Nebat, da kiba u la pynleh pop ïa ki Israel; um shym kynriah na kita.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ka jingbitar U Trai ka la meh ding ïa ki Israel bad u la aiti ïa ki borabor ha ka kti u Hasael u syiem ka Syria, bad ha ka kti u Benhadad u khun u Hasael.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te u Jehoahas u la kyrpad ïa U Trai, bad U Trai u la shahshkor ïa u; naba u la ïohi ïa ka jingbanbeiñ ïa ki Israel, kumno ba u syiem ka Syria u la banbeiñ ïa ki.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> (U Trai te u la ai u nongpynim ha ki Israel, kumta, ki la lait na ka kti ki Syria: bad ki khun Israel ki la ïashong ha la ki ïingjaiñ, kumba mynshuwa.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> La kumta ruh, kim shym kynriah noh na ki pop ka ïing u Jeroboam, da kiba u la pynleh pop ïa ki Israel, hynrei, ki la ïaid ha ki: bad ki Asherah ruh ki la dang sah ha Samaria.)",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Naba um shym la pynsah briew ha u Jehoahas, hynrei, tang sanphew ki nongshong kulai, bad shiphew tylli ki kali, bad shiphew hajar ki nongïaleh na tbian; naba u syiem ka Syria u la pynduh khoit ïa ki, bad u la pynlong ïa ki kum u pui pui haba shoh kba.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Jehoahas, bad baroh kaba u la leh, bad ka bor jong u, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ki Israel?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u Jehoahas u la thiah bad la ki kpa; bad ki la tep ïa u ha Samaria: bad u Jehoash u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ha ka balaiphew hynñiew snem u Joash u syiem ka Judah, u Jehoash u khun u Jehoahas u la sdang ban synshar halor ki Israel ha Samaria, bad u la synshar khathynriew snem.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai; um shym kynriah noh na ki pop baroh ki jong u Jeroboam u khun u Nebat, da kiba u la pynleh pop ïa ki Israel: hynrei, u la ïaid ha ki.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Joash, bad baroh kaba u la leh, bad ka bor jong u da kaba u ïaleh thma ïa u Amasaïah u syiem ka Judah, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ki Israel?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Joash u la thiah bad la ki kpa; bad u Jeroboam u la shong halor ka khet jong u: bad la tep ïa u Joash ha Samaria bad ki syiem ki Israel.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u Elisha u la pang na kata ka jingpang ba u la ïap: bad u Jehoash u syiem ki Israel u la wan hiar ha u, bad u la ïam ïa u, bad u la ong, “Ko kpa, ko kpa, ki kali Israel bad ki nongshong kulai jong ki!”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u Elisha u la ong ha u, “To shim ka ryntieh bad ki khnam”: bad u la shim ha u ka ryntieh bad ki khnam.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te u la ong ha u syiem ki Israel, “To buh ïa la ka kti ha ka ryntieh:” te u la buh ïa la ka kti. Bad u Elisha u la buh ïa la ki kti halor ki kti u syiem.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U la ong ruh, “To plie ïa ka jingkhang ïit kaba shaphang mihngi”: bad u la plie ïa ka. Ynda kumta, u Elisha u la ong, “To siat”: te u la siat. U ong te, “U khnam ka jingjop U Trai, u khnam ka jingjop halor ka Syria keiñ: naba men pom ïa ki Syria ha Aphek, ha ban da me la pynduh noh ïa ki.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u la ong ruh, “To shim ki khnam”: te u la shim ïa ki. U la ong te ha u syiem ki Israel, “To shoh ïa ka khyndew”: u te u la shoh lai wat, bad u la keiñ noh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te u briew jong U Blei u la bitar ïa u, bad u la ong, “Hynrei, me la dei ban shoh san wat hynriew wat; kumta men da la jop ïa ka Syria ha ban da me la pynduh noh ïa ka: naba kumta te, men jop ïa ka Syria tang lai wat.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u Elisha u la ïap, bad ki la tep ïa u. Mynta ki kynhun ki Moab ki la ïahiar thma ha kaba sdang ka snem.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te katba ki la dang ïatep ïa u briew, ha khmih, ki la ïohi ïa ka kynhun; bad ki la ïabred ïa uta u briew ha ka jingtep u Elisha: te tang ba uta u briew u shu dei ha ki shyieng u Elisha u la im pat, bad u la ïeng joit da la ki kjat.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Hasael u syiem ka Syria u la banbeiñ ïa ki Israel ha ki sngi u Jehoahas baroh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Hynrei, U Trai u la leh sbun ïa ki, u la isynei ïa ki, bad u la khmih ïa ki, na ka bynta ka jutang jong u bad u Abraham, bad u Isaak, bad u Jakob, bad un ym pynduh khoit ïa ki, lymne haduh mynta um pat bred ïa ki na khmat jong u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te u Hasael u syiem ka Syria u la ïap: bad u Benhadad u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u Jehoash u khun u Jehoahas u la knieh pat na ka kti u Benhadad u khun u Hasael ïa kita ki shnong kiba u la lah knieh ha ka thma na ka kti u Jehoahas u kpa jong u. Lai wat u Joash u la jop ïa u, bad u la ïoh pat ïa kita ki shnong jong ki Israel."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ha ka snem ka ba-ar jong u Joash u khun u Jehoahas u syiem ki Israel, u Amasaïah u khun u Joash u syiem ka Judah u la sdang ban synshar.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U la long arphew san snem ka rta mynba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar arphew khyndai snem ha Jerusalem: bad ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka la long “ka Jehoaddan” kaba na Jerusalem.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u la leh ïa kata kaba dei ha khmat U Trai, hynrei, ym kum u Dabid u kpa jong u: u la leh katba kum kata baroh ba u Joash u kpa jong u, u la leh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> La kumta ruh, ym shym la pynduh noh ïa kita ki jaka bajrong: ki briew ki la dang kñia bad ki thang ka jingiwbih ha kita ki jaka bajrong.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te tang shu la pynskhem ïa ka hima ha ka kti jong u, u la pynïap ïa kita ki shakri jong u kiba la lah pynïap ïa u syiem u kpa jong u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei, um shym la pynïap ïa ki khun kita ki nongpynïap: katba kum kata ba la thoh ha Ka Kitab Ka Hukum u Moses, kumba U Trai u la hukum, u da ong, “Ïa ki kpa yn ym pynïap na ka bynta ki khun, lymne ïa ki khun yn ym pynïap na ka bynta ki kpa; hynrei, u briew baroh un ïap namar la ka jong hi ka pop.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U la pynïap na ki Edom ha ka Them Mluh shiphew hajar ngut, bad u la jop ïa ka Selah ha ka thma, bad u la khot kyrteng ïa ka, “ka Jokthil” haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ynda kumta, u Amasaïah u la phah ki nonglam-ktien ha u Jehoash, u khun u Jehoahas u khun u Jehu, u syiem ki Israel, u da ong, “Ale, ngin thaw ïakhmih markhmat.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Jehoash u syiem ki Israel u la jubab ïa u Amasaïah u syiem ka Judah, u da ong, “U dieng shiah uba ha Lebanon u la phah ha u dieng Kedar uba ha Lebanon, u da ong, ‘To buh kurim ïa la ka khun ha u khun jong nga:’ hynrei, u mrad khlaw uba ha Lebanon u la ïaid nangta, bad u la ïuh roit ïa uta u dieng shiah.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Shisha me la jop ïa ka Edom, bad ka dohnud jong me ka la pynsngew meng ïa me: to sngewsarong ha kata, bad to sah ha la ïing namar balei men leh lushia ïa ka ban sniew, ba men kyllon, ma me keiñ, bad ka Judah lem bad me?”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hynrei, u Amasaïah um sngap. Kumta u Jehoash u syiem ki Israel u la leit kiew; bad ma u lem bad u Amasaïah u syiem ka Judah ki la ïakhmih markhmat ha Beth-shemesh, kaba dei ïa ka Judah.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ïa ka Judah te la jop ha khmat ki Israel; bad ki la phet ïap uwei uwei baroh sha la ka ïingjaiñ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u Jehoash u syiem ki Israel u la kem ïa u Amasaïah u syiem ka Judah, u khun u Jehoash u khun u Ahasaïah, ha Beth-shemesh, bad haba u la wan sha Jerusalem, u la pynkyllon ïa ka kynroh ka Jerusalem naduh ka khyrdop Ephraim haduh ka khyrdop ka dong, sawspah pruh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u la shim ïa ka ksiar bad ka rupa baroh, bad ïa ki pliang baroh katba la shem ha ka ïing U Trai, bad ha ki jingkynshew ka ïingsyiem, ïa ki nongbahjamin ruh, bad u la leit phai sha Samaria.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Jehoash kiba u la leh, bad ka bor jong u, bad kumno u la ïaleh thma bad u Amasaïah u syiem ka Judah, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ki Israel?",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u Jehoash u la thiah bad la ki kpa, bad la tep ïa u ha Samaria bad ki syiem ki Israel; bad u Jeroboam u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u Amasaïah u khun u Jehoash u syiem ka Judah u la im, ynda la ïap u Jehoash u khun u Jehoahas u syiem ki Israel, khatsan snem.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Amasaïah, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ka Judah?",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ki la ïashet ïa u ha Jerusalem; te u la phet ïap sha Lakhish: hynrei, ki la phah hadien jong u sha Lakhish, bad ki la pynïap ïa u hangta.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ki la wallam ïa u halor ki kulai: bad la tep ïa u ha Jerusalem lem bad la ki kpa ha ka shnong u Dabid.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te u paidbah Judah baroh u la shim ïa u Asariah, uba la long khathynriew snem ka rta, bad ki la thung syiem ïa u ha ka jaka u kpa jong u, u Amasaïah.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> U la tei ïa ka Elath, bad u la pynïoh pat ïa ka ha Judah, hadien kata, u syiem u la thiah bad la ki kpa.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ha ka snem ka bakhatsan u Amasaïah u khun u Joash u syiem ka Judah, u Jeroboam u khun u Joash u syiem ki Israel u la sdang ban synshar ha Samaria, bad u la synshar sawphew wei snem.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai: um shym kynriah noh na ki pop baroh u Jeroboam u khun u Nebat, da kiba u la pynleh pop ïa ki Israel.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> U la pynïoh pat ka pud ki Israel naduh kaba leit rung sha Hamath haduh ka duriaw ka Arabah, kat kum ka ktien U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, kaba u la kren da ka kti u shakri jong u, u Jonah u khun u Amittai, u nongïathuhlypa, uba na Gath-hepher.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Naba U Trai u la ïohi ïa ka jingshitom ki Israel, ba ka la kthang eh: naba ym don ba la ker kut lymne ba sah laitluid, lymne ym shym la don u nongïarap ïa ki Israel.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te U Trai um shym ong ba un pyndam noh ïa ka kyrteng ki Israel napoh ka bneng: hynrei, u la pynim ïa ki da ka kti u Jeroboam u khun u Joash.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Jeroboam, bad baroh kaba u la leh, bad ka bor jong u, kumno u la ïaleh thma, bad kumno u la pynïoh pat ha ki Israel ïa ka Damaskos bad ka Hamath, kiba la ju dei ki jong ka Judah, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ki Israel?",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te u Jeroboam u la thiah bad la ki kpa, bad ki syiem ki Israel keiñ: bad u Sekharaïah u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ha ka snem arphew hynñiew jong u Jeroboam u syiem ki Israel, u Asaraïah u khun u Amasaïah, u syiem ka Judah u la sdang ban synshar.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U la long khathynriew snem ka rta mynba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar sanphew ar snem ha Jerusalem: bad ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka la long “ka Jekoliah” kaba na Jerusalem.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u la leh ïa kata kaba dei ha khmat U Trai, kat kum kata baroh ba u kpa jong u, u Amasaïah u la lah leh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> La kumta ruh, ym shym pynduh noh ïa ki jaka bajrong: ki briew ki la dang kñia bad ki thang jingiwbih ha ki jaka bajrong.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te U Trai u la shoh ïa u syiem, ba u la long u bapang 'ñiangthohlieh ha ban da u ïap, bad u la shong ha ka ïing kaba kyrpang. Bad u Jotham u khun u syiem u la long halor ka ïingsyiem, u da bishar ïa ki briew jong kata ka ri.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Asaraïah, bad baroh kaba u la leh, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ka Judah?",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U Asaraïah te u la thiah bad la ki kpa; bad ki la tep ïa u bad la ki kpa ha ka shnong u Dabid: bad u Jotham u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ha ka snem laiphew phra jong u Asaraïah u syiem ka Judah, u Sekharaïah u khun u Jeroboam u la synshar halor ki Israel ha Samaria hynriew bnai.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai, kumba la leh ki kpa jong u: um shym kynriah na ki pop u Jeroboam u khun u Nebat, da kiba u la pynleh pop ïa ki Israel.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Shallum u khun u Jabesh u la ïashet ïa u, bad u la pom ïa u ha khmat u paidbah, bad u la pynïap ïa u, bad u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Sekharaïah, ha khmih, la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ki Israel.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kane ka la long ka ktien U Trai kaba u la kren ha u Jehu, u da ong, “Ki khun jong me haduh ka basaw pateng kin shong halor ka khet ki Israel.” Te ka la long kumta.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U Shallum u khun u Jabesh u la sdang ban synshar ha ka snem laiphew khyndai jong u Ussiah u syiem ka Judah; bad u la synshar shi bnai ha Samaria.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u Menahem u khun u Gadi u la leit kiew na Tirsah, bad haba u la poi ha Samaria, u la pom ïa u Shallum u khun u Jabesh ha Samaria, bad u la pynïap ïa u, bad u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Shallum, bad kata ka jingïashet jong u kaba u la pynlong, ha khmih, la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ki Israel.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ynda kumta, u Menahem u la pom ïa ka Tiphsah, bad ïa baroh kiba don ha ka, bad ïa ki pud jong ka, naduh Tirsah: namar ba kim shym la plie ïa u, namar kata, u la pom ïa ka; bad ïa ki kynthei kiba ha ka baroh kiba la punkhun u la tar noh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ha ka snem laiphew khyndai jong u Asaraïah u syiem ka Judah, u Menahem u khun u Gadi u la sdang ban synshar halor ki Israel, bad u la synshar shiphew snem ha Samaria.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai: um shym kynriah baroh ki sngi jong u na ki pop u Jeroboam u khun u Nebat, da kiba u la pynleh pop ïa ki Israel.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te u Pul u syiem ka Assyria u la wan ïaleh ïa kata ka ri; te u Menahem u la ai ïa u Pul shi hajar ki talent rupa, ba ka kti jong u kan ïoh long lem bad u ïa ka ban pynskhem ïa ka hima ha ka kti jong u.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Menahem u la khrong ïa uta u sbai na ki Israel, na kiba khraw spah baroh keiñ, na uwei uwei u briew sanphew shekel ka rupa, ban ai ha u syiem ka Assyria. Kumta u syiem ka Assyria u la leit phai pat, bad um shym la sah shuh hangta ha kata ka ri.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Menahem, bad baroh kaba u la leh, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ki Israel?",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Menahem u la thiah bad la ki kpa; bad u Pekahiah u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ha ka snem sanphew jong u Asaraïah u syiem ka Judah, u Pekahiah u khun u Menahem u la sdang ban synshar halor ki Israel ha Samaria, bad u la synshar ar snem.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai: um shym kynriah na ki pop u Jeroboam u khun u Nebat, da kiba u la pynleh pop ïa ki Israel.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te u Pekah u khun u Remaliah, u kaptan jong u, u la ïashet ïa u, bad u la pom ïa u ha Samaria, ha ka kut ka ïingsyiem, lem bad u Argob bad u Arieh; te la don lem bad u sanphew ngut ki nong Gilead: bad haba u la pynïap ïa u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Pekahiah, bad baroh kaba u la leh, ha khmih, la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ki Israel.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ha ka snem sanphew ar u Asaraïah u syiem ka Judah, u Pekah u khun u Remaliah u la sdang ban synshar halor ki Israel ha Samaria, bad u la synshar arphew snem.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai: um shym kynriah na ki pop u Jeroboam u khun u Nebat, da kiba u la pynleh pop ïa ki Israel.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ha ki sngi jong u Pekah u syiem ki Israel, u la wan u Tiglath-pilesar u syiem ka Assyria bad u la jop ïa ka Ijon, bad ïa ka Abel-beth-maakah, bad ka Janoah, bad ka Kedesh, bad ka Hasor, bad ka Gilead, bad ïa ka Galilaïa, ka ri Naphtali baroh keiñ; bad u la ring mraw ïa ki sha ri Assyria.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te u Hoshea u khun u Elah u la pynlong ka jingïashet ïa u Pekah u khun u Remaliah, te haba u la pom ïa u, u la pynïap ïa u, bad u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u, ha ka ba-arphew snem jong u Jotham u khun u Ussiah.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Pekah, bad baroh kaba u la leh, ha khmih, la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ki Israel.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ha ka snem ka ba-ar jong u Pekah u khun u Remaliah u syiem ki Israel, u Jotham u khun u Ussiah u syiem ka Judah u la sdang ban synshar.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> U la long arphew san snem ka rta mynba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar khathynriew snem ha Jerusalem: bad ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka la long “ka Jerusha” ka khun u Sadok.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te u la leh ïa kata kaba dei ha khmat U Trai: u la leh katba kum kata baroh ba la leh u kpa jong u, u Ussiah.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> La kumta ïa ki jaka bajrong ym shym la pynduh noh: ki briew ki la dang kñia bad thang jingiwbih ha ki jaka bajrong. U la tei ïa ka khyrdop kaba kham shaneng jong ka ïing U Trai.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Jotham, bad kaba u la leh baroh, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ka Judah?",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ha kita ki sngi, U Trai u la sdang ban phah ïaleh ïa ki Judah da u Resin u syiem ka Syria, bad da u Pekah u khun u Remaliah.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Te u Jotham u la thiah bad la ki kpa, bad la tep ïa u bad la ki kpa ha ka shnong u Dabid u kpa jong u; bad u Ahas u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ha ka snem khathynñiew u Pekah u khun u Remaliah, u Ahas u khun u Jotham u syiem ka Judah u la sdang ban synshar.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U Ahas u la long arphew snem mynba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar khathynriew snem ha Jerusalem: te um shym la leh ïa kata kaba dei ha khmat U Trai U Blei jong u, kum u Dabid u kpa jong u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hynrei, u la ïaid ha ka lynti ki syiem ki Israel, bad nalor kata, u la pynïaid ïa la u khun lyngba ka ding, kat kum ki jingijli jong kiba mane bleithaw, ïa kiba U Trai u la beh noh na khmat ki khun Israel.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u la kñia bad u la thang ka jingiwbih ruh ha ki jaka bajrong, bad ha ki lum rit, bad hapoh u dieng bajyrngam baroh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ynda kumta, u Resin u syiem ka Syria bad u Pekah u khun u Remaliah u syiem ki Israel ki la ïawan kiew ban ïaleh thma ïa ka Jerusalem: bad ki la ker kut ïa u Ahas, hynrei, kim lah ban jop ïa u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ha kata ka por, u Resin u syiem ka Syria u la pynïoh pat ïa ka Elath sha ka Syria, bad u la beh noh ïa ki Jiw na Elath: te ki Syria ki la leit sha Elath, bad ki la shong hangta, haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kumta, u Ahas u la phah ki nonglam-ktien sha u Tiglath-pilesar u syiem ka Assyria, u da ong, “Nga long u shakri jong me bad u khun jong me: to wan kiew, bad pyllait ïa nga na ka kti u syiem ka Syria, bad na ka kti u syiem ki Israel kiba ïeng ïaleh ïa nga.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Ahas u la shim ïa ka rupa bad ka ksiar kaba la shem ha ka ïing U Trai, bad ha ki jingkynshew ka ïing u syiem, bad u la phah ïa ki kum ka jingai sngewbha ha u syiem ka Assyria.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U syiem ka Assyria te u la shahshkor ïa u: bad u syiem ka Assyria u la leit kiew ban ïaleh ïa ka Damaskos, te haba u la jop ïa ka, u la ring mraw ïa ki briew sha Kir, bad u la pynïap ïa u Resin ruh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u syiem Ahas u la leit sha Damaskos ban ïashem ïa u Tiglath-pilesar u syiem ka Assyria, bad u la ïohi ïa ka duwan kaba don ha Damaskos: te u syiem Ahas u la phah ha u Urijah lyngdoh ïa ka dur jong kata ka duwan, bad ïa ka nuksa jong ka, kumba la thaw ïa ka baroh.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u Urijah lyngdoh u la tei ïa ka duwan: kat kum kata baroh ba la phah u syiem Ahas na Damaskos, kumta, u Urijah lyngdoh u la thaw hamar kaba u la wan u syiem Ahas na Damaskos.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ynda u syiem u la wan na Damaskos, u syiem u la ïohi ïa kata ka duwan: bad u syiem u la leit hajan kata ka duwan, bad u la ainguh halor jong ka.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u la thang ïa ka jingainguh thang jong u bad ïa la ka jingainguh bam, bad u la theh ïa la ka jingainguh dih, bad u la synreit ka snam ki jingainguh pynïasuk jong u, halor kata ka duwan.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te ïa kata ka duwan rnong, kaba la don ha khmat U Trai, u la wallam na khmat ka ïing, napdeng ka duwan jong u bad ka ïing U Trai, bad u la buh ïa ka shaphang shatei ka duwan jong u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> U syiem Ahas te u la hukum ïa u Urijah lyngdoh, u da ong, “Halor ka duwan bakhraw men thang ïa ka jingainguh thang mynstep, bad ïa ka jingainguh bam la janmiet, bad ïa ka jingainguh thang u syiem, bad ka jingainguh bam jong u, lem bad ki jingainguh thang jong ki briew ka ri baroh, bad ka jingainguh bam jong ki, bad ka jingainguh dih jong ki; bad men synreit halor jong ka, ïa ka snam baroh jong ka jingainguh thang, bad ïa ka snam baroh jong ka jingkñia: hynrei, ka duwan rnong kan long ïa nga ban ïakylli da ka.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kumne u Urijah lyngdoh u la leh, kat kum kata baroh ba u syiem Ahas u la hukum.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u syiem Ahas u la loit noh ïa ki shrong na ki jingpynshong, bad u la pynhiar noh ïa ka dabor nalor jong ki; ïa kata ka duriaw ruh u la pynhiar nalor kita ki masi dab rnong kiba la don hapoh jong ka, bad u la buh ïa ka halor ka jaka ba la siang maw.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ïa ka lynti ba la tap na ka bynta ka Sabbaton kaba ki la tei ha kata ka ïing, bad ïa ka lynti rung u syiem na shabar, u la pynkylla sha ka ïing U Trai, namar u syiem ka Assyria.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Ahas kiba u la leh, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ka Judah?",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Ahas u la thiah bad la ki kpa, bad la tep ïa u bad la ki kpa ha ka shnong u Dabid: bad u Hesekaïah u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ha ka snem ka bakhat-ar jong u Ahas u syiem ka Judah, u Hoshea u khun u Elah u la sdang ban synshar ha Samaria halor ki Israel, bad u la synshar khyndai snem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai, hynrei, ym kum kita ki syiem ki Israel kiba la mynshuwa jong u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U Shalmanesar u syiem ka Assyria u la wan kiew ban ïaleh ïa u; te u Hoshea u la kylla long u shakri jong u, bad u la wallam ki jingai sngewbha ïa u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te u syiem ka Assyria u shem ka jingshet ha u Hoshea; naba u la lah phah ki nonglam-ktien ha u So u syiem ka Ijipt, bad um shym la ai ka jingai sngewbha ha u syiem ka Assyria, kumba u ju leh man ka snem: namar kata, u syiem ka Assyria u la set kut ïa u, bad u la khum ïa u ha byndi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem ka Assyria u la wan kiew lyngba ka ri baroh, te haba u la leit kiew sha Samaria, u la ker kut ïa ka lai snem.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ha ka snem ka bakhyndai jong u Hoshea, u syiem ka Assyria u la jop ïa ka Samaria, te ynda la ring mraw ïa ki Israel sha ka ri Assyria, u la pynshong ïa ki ha Halah, bad ha Habor, ha ka wah Gosan, bad ha ki shnong jong ki Mid.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ka la jia kumta, namar ki khun Israel ki la leh pop ïa U Trai U Blei jong ki, uba la wallam ïa ki na ka ri Ijipt napoh ka kti u Pharaoh u syiem ka Ijipt, bad ki la sheptieng ïa kiwei pat ki blei,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad ki la ïaid ha ki hukum kita ki jaid bynriew, ïa kiba U Trai u la beh noh na khmat ki khun Israel, bad ki jong ki syiem ki Israel, kiba ki la pynlong.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad ki khun Israel ha kaba rieh ki la leh ïa kiei kiei ki bymdei, pyrshah ïa U Trai U Blei jong ki, bad ki la thaw ha ki, ïa ki jaka bajrong ha ki shnong jong ki baroh, naduh ka kut ki nongap haduh ka shnong ba la ker kynroh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ki la pynïeng ha ki, ïa ki durblei bad ki Asherah halor u lum bajrong baroh, bad hapoh u dieng bajyrngam baroh:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> hangta te ki la thang ïa ka jingiwbih ha ki jaka bajrong baroh, kumba la leh kita ki jaid bynriew ïa kiba U Trai u la rong noh ha shuwa jong ki; bad ki la leh ïa kita ki bymman ban pankwah ïa U Trai ban bitar:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> bad ki la shakri ruh ïa ki durblei, ïa kiba U Trai u la lah ong ïa ki, “Phin ym leh ïa kane.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, U Trai u la phla ha u Israel, bad ha u Judah, da ka kti u nongïathuhlypa baroh, bad da u nongïohi baroh, u da ong, “To phai phi na ki lynti basniew jong phi, bad sumar ïa ki hukum jong nga bad ïa ki aiñ jong nga, kat kum kata ka hukum baroh kaba nga la hukum ïa ki kpa jong phi, bad ïa kiba nga la phah ha phi da ka kti ki shakri jong nga ki nongïathuhlypa.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Pynban, kim treh ban sngap, hynrei, ki la pyneh ïa la ka ryndang, kum ka ryndang ki kpa jong ki, ki bym shym la ngeit ha U Trai U Blei jong ki.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ki la kyntait ïa ki aiñ jong u bad ïa ka jutang jong u, kiba u la pynlong bad ki kpa jong ki, bad ïa ki jingphla jong u, kiba u la phla ha ki; bad ki la bud ïa ka jingthala, bad ki la kylla long thala, bad ki la leit bud ïa kita ki kynja bynriew kiba la don baroh sawdong jong ki, shaphang kiba U Trai u la lah adong ïa ki ba kin ym leh kum kita.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ki la lyndet ruh ïa ki hukum U Trai U Blei jong ki baroh, bad ki la thaw ha ki, ki dur ba la saiñ, ar tylli ki khun masi keiñ, bad ki la pynlong ïa ki Asherah, bad ki la mane ïa u paidbah bneng baroh, bad ki la shakri ïa u Baal.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ki la pynïaid ïa la ki khun shynrang bad kynthei lyngba ka ding, bad ki la don ki jingleh byrtong bad ki jingleh myntor, bad ki la die ïa lade ban leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai, ban pankwah ïa u ban bitar.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Namar kata, U Trai u la bitar eh bad ki Israel, bad u la pynkynriah ïa ki na khmat jong u: ym don ba sah shuh sa tang ka jaid Judah hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ki Judah ruh kim shym la sumar ïa ki hukum U Trai U Blei jong ki, hynrei, ki la ïaid ha ki aiñ ki Israel ïa kiba ki la pynlong.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te U Trai u la kyntait ïa u symbai ki Israel baroh, bad u la pynshitom ïa ki, bad u la ai noh ïa ki ha ka kti ki nonglute, haduh ba u la bred ïa ki na khmat jong u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Naba u la kad ïa ki Israel na ka ïing u Dabid; bad ki la pynlong syiem ïa u Jeroboam u khun u Nebat: te u Jeroboam u la pynbakla ïa ki Israel na kaba bud ïa U Trai, bad u la pynleh pop ïa ki, ka pop kaba kham khraw keiñ.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad ki khun Israel ki la ïaid ha ki pop u Jeroboam kiba u la leh baroh; kim shym kynriah noh na ki;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> ha ban da U Trai u la pynkynriah noh ïa ki Israel na khmat jong u, kumba u la kren da ka kti ki shakri jong u ki nongïathuhlypa baroh. Kumta, la ring noh ïa ki Israel na ka ri jong ki sha Assyria, haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u syiem ka Assyria u la wallam ïa ki briew na Babilon, bad na Kuthah, bad na Abba, bad na Hamath, bad Sepharbaim, bad u la pynshong ïa ki ha ki shnong ka Samaria ha ka jaka ki khun Israel: bad ki la ïoh duh ïa ka ri Samaria, bad ki la shong ha ki shnong jong ka.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te ka la long, hamar kaba ki sdang ban shong hangta, ba kim shym sheptieng ïa U Trai: namar kata, U Trai u la phah ki sing hapdeng jong ki, kiba la pynïap katto katne na ki.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Namar kata, ki la kren ha u syiem ka Assyria, ki da ong, “Kita ki jaid bynriew kiba me la ring noh, bad me la pynshong ha ki shnong Samaria, kim tip ïa ka rukom U Blei jong ka ri: namar kata, u la phah ki sing hapdeng jong ki, te, ha khmih, ki la pynïap ïa ki, namar kim tip ïa ka rukom U Blei jong ka ri.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem ka Assyria u la hukum, u da ong, “Leit lam shata uwei na ki lyngdoh ba phi la wallam nangta; bad to kin leit shong hangta, bad to un hikai ïa ki, ïa ka rukom U Blei jong ka ri.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kumta, uwei na ki lyngdoh ba ki la ring noh na Samaria u la wan shong ha Bethel, bad u la hikai ïa ki, kumno ki dei ban sheptieng ïa U Trai.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> La kumta man la ka jaid bynriew ka la thaw la ki jong ki blei, bad ki la buh ïa ki ha kita ki ïing ki jaka bajrong ïa kiba ki Samaria ki la lah thaw, man la ka jaid bynriew ha la ki shnong ha kiba ki shong.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te ki Babilon ki la pynlong ïa u Sukkoth-benoth, bad ki nong Kuth ki la pynlong ïa u Nergal, bad ki nong Hamath ki la pynlong ïa u Ashima,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> bad ki nong Abbim ki la pynlong ïa u Nibhas bad ïa u Tartak, bad ki nong Sephar ki la thang ïa la ki khun ha ka ding ha u Adrammelek bad ka Anammelek, ki blei jong ka Sepharbaim.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Kumta, ki la sheptieng ïa U Trai, bad ki la pynlong ha ki napdeng jong ki hi ki lyngdoh ïa ki jaka bajrong, kiba la kñia na ka bynta jong ki ha kita ki ïing ki jaka bajrong.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ki la sheptieng ïa U Trai, bad ki la shakri ïa ki blei jong ki hi, katba kum ka rukom kita ki jaid bynriew napdeng jong kiba la lah ring noh ïa ki.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Haduh kane ka sngi ki leh kat kum ki rukom bamynshuwa: Kim sheptieng ïa U Trai, lymne kim leh kat kum ki aiñ jong ki, lane kat kum ki rukom jong ki, lane kat kum ka adong lane kat kum ka hukum kaba U Trai u la hukum ïa ki khun u Jakob, ïa uba u la kyrteng “Israel”:",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> bad kiba U Trai u la lah pynlong ka jutang, bad u la hukum skhem ïa ki, u da ong, “Phin ym sheptieng ïa kiwei pat ki blei, lymne dem ïa lade ha ki, lymne shakri ïa ki, lymne kñia ha ki:",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> hynrei, U Trai, uba la wallam ïa phi na ka ri Ijipt da ka bor bah bad da ka ksang'ti ba la kner, ïa uta keiñ, phin sheptieng, bad ha u phin dem ïa lade, bad ha u phin kñia:",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> bad ïa ki aiñ bad ïa ki rukom, bad ïa ka adong bad ïa ka hukum, kiba u la thoh ïa phi, phin sumar ban leh ha la ka rta; bad phin ym sheptieng ïa kiwei pat ki blei:",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> bad ïa kata ka jutang kaba nga la pynlong bad phi phin ym klet; lymne sheptieng ïa kiwei pat ki blei:",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> hynrei, ïa U Trai uba U Blei jong phi keiñ, phin sheptieng; te un pyllait ïa phi na ka kti ki nongshun jong phi baroh.”",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Pynban, kim shym sngap, hynrei, ki la leh kat kum ka rukom jong kiba mynshuwa.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Kumta, kine ki jaid bynriew ki la sheptieng ïa U Trai, bad ki la shakri ruh ïa ki durblei ba la thaw; ki khun jong ki ruh kumjuh, bad ki khun ki khun jong ki, kumba la leh ki kpa jong ki, kumta hi ki leh haduh kane ka sngi."
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ha ka snem ka balai jong u Hoshea u khun u Elah u syiem ki Israel, u Hesekaïah u khun u Ahas u syiem ka Judah u la sdang ban synshar.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U la long arphew san snem ka rta mynba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar arphew khyndai snem ha Jerusalem: ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u te ka la long “ka Abi” ka khun u Sekharaïah.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u la leh ïa kata kaba dei ha khmat U Trai, kat kum kata baroh kaba u Dabid u kpa jong u, u la leh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> U la pynduh noh ïa ki jaka bajrong, bad u la pynkyllon ïa ki païa, bad u la khet noh ïa ki Asherah: bad u la pynkheiñ noh lyngkhot lyngkhai ïa uta u 'seiñ rnong ba u Moses u la lah thaw; naba haduh kita ki sngi, ki khun Israel ki la thang jingiwbih ïa u: bad la khot ïa u, “u Nehushtan”.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U la shaniah ha U Trai, U Blei ki Israel; kumta ba hadien jong u ym shym la don uwei kum ma u hapdeng ki syiem ka Judah baroh, lymne hapdeng kita kiba la mynshuwa jong u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Naba u la snoh ha U Trai, um shym kynriah noh na kaba bud ïa U, hynrei, u la sumar ïa ki hukum jong U, kiba U Trai u la hukum ha u Moses.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U Trai u la don lem bad u: kat shaba u leit u man bha: bad u la ïaleh pyrshah ïa u syiem ka Assyria, bad um shym shakri ïa u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U la jop ïa ki Philistia, haduh Gasa bad ki pud jong ka, naduh ka kut ki nongap haduh ka shnong ba la ker kut.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ha ka snem ka basaw jong u syiem Hesekaïah, kaba long ka snem bahynñiew jong u Hoshea u khun u Elah u syiem ki Israel, u Shalmanesar u syiem ka Assyria u la wan kiew ban ïaleh ïa ka Samaria, bad u la ker kut ïa ka.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ha ka bakut ki lai snem, ki la jop ïa ka: ha ka snem ka bahynriew jong u Hesekaïah keiñ, kaba la long ka snem bakhyndai jong u Hoshea u syiem ki Israel, la jop ïa ka Samaria.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u syiem ka Assyria u la ring noh ïa ki Israel sha Assyria, bad u la pynshong ïa ki ha Halah, bad ha Habor, harud ka wah Gosan, bad ha ki shnong ki Mid:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> namar kim shym kohnguh ïa ka ktien U Trai U Blei jong ki, hynrei, ki la ryngkang ïa ka jutang jong u, ïa kata baroh keiñ kaba u Moses u shakri U Trai u la hukum, bad kim treh ban sngap ïa ka, lymne ban leh ïa ka.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ha ka snem ka bakhatsaw jong u syiem Hesekaïah, u Sennakherib u syiem ka Assyria u la wan kiew ban ïaleh ïa ki shnong ba la ker kut jong ka Judah baroh, bad u la jop ïa ki.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u Hesekaïah u syiem ka Judah u la phah ha u syiem ka Assyria ha Lakhish, u da ong, “Nga la palat; to leit phai na nga: ïa kaba men buh ha nga ngan shah.” Bad u syiem ka Assyria u la buh halor u Hesekaïah u syiem ka Judah laispah ki talent rupa bad laiphew ki talent ksiar.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u Hesekaïah u la ai ïa u ïa ka rupa baroh katba la shem ha ka ïing U Trai, bad ha ki jingkynshew ka ïing u syiem.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ha kata ka por, u Hesekaïah u la law noh ïa ka ksiar na ki jingkhang ka templ jong U Trai, bad na ki rishot kiba u Hesekaïah u syiem ka Judah u la sah ksiar, bad u la ai ïa ka ha u syiem ka Assyria.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u syiem ka Assyria u la phah ïa u Tartan bad u Rab-saris bad u Rabshakeh na Lakhish ha u syiem Hesekaïah ha Jerusalem bad u paidïapom babun. Te haba ki la leit kiew ki la wan poi sha Jerusalem. Te ynda ki la wan kiew, ki la poi bad ki la ïeng hajan ka lynti um ka nan kaba shaneng, kaba long ha ka lynti bah ka lyngkha u nongpynkhuid jaiñ.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te ynda ki la khot ïa u syiem, la wan mih ha ki u Eliakim u khun u Hilkiah, uba halor ka ïing, bad u Shebnah u nongthoh, bad u Joah u khun u Asaph u nongthoh rekord.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te u Rabshakeh u la ong ha ki, “To ong mynta ha u Hesekaïah, ‘Kumne ong uta u syiem bakhraw, u syiem ka Assyria keiñ, “Ka jingshaniah aïu kane ha kaba me shaniah?”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Me ong, “hynrei, ki long tang ki ktien duh ei: don ka buit bad ka bor ban ïaleh thma.” Hato hano me shaniah, ba me la ïaleh pyrshah ïa nga?",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te, ha khmih, me shaniah ha u diengduh jong une u khah ba la kheiñ, ha ka Ijipt keiñ; ha uba lada u briew u shaniah, un tar ïa ka kti jong u, bad un peib'la: kumta u Pharaoh u syiem ka Ijipt u long ha kita baroh kiba shaniah ha u.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hynrei, lada phi ong ha nga, “Ngi shaniah ha U Trai U Blei jong ngi”: uta um long uba ki jaka bajrong jong u bad ki duwan jong u, u Hesekaïah u la pynduh noh, bad u la ong ha ka Judah bad ha ka Jerusalem, “Phin mane ha khmat kane ka duwan ha Jerusalem?”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Namar kata te, nga kyrpad ïa phi, to ai synjat ha u kynrad jong nga u syiem ka Assyria, bad nga ngan ai ha me ar hajar ki kulai, lada ha ka liang jong me, me lah ban buh ki nongshong halor jong ki.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kumno te me lah ban pynphai noh ïa ka khmat uwei u kaptan uba rit tam na ki shakri u kynrad jong nga, bad ban shaniah ha ka Ijipt ban ïoh kali bad nongshong kulai?",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hato nga wan kiew khlem U Trai pyrshah ïa kane ka jaka ban pynduh ïa ka? U Trai u la ong ha nga, “Khie leit ïaleh ïa kane ka ri, bad pynduh ïa ka.” ’ ”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ynda kumta, u Eliakim u khun u Hilkiah, bad u Shebnah, bad u Joah, ki la ong ha u Rabshakeh, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to kren ha la ki shakri ha ka ktien Syria; naba ngi sngewthuh ïa kata: bad wat kren ha ngi ha ka ktien ki Jiw, ha kaba ïohsngew ki briew kiba don ha ka kynroh.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Hynrei, u Rabshakeh u la ong ha ki, “Hato u kynrad jong nga u la phah ïa nga mo ha u kynrad jong me, bad ha me, ban kren ïa kine ki ktien? um shym la phah ïa nga ha kita ki briew kiba shong ha kata ka kynroh, ba kin dup bam ïa la ka kaibri, bad dih ïa la ka umjung bad phi?”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ynda kumta, u Rabshakeh u la ïeng bad u la pyrta da ka ktien bajam ha ka ktien ki Jiw bad u la kren, u da ong, “To sngew phi ïa ka ktien uta u syiem bakhraw, u syiem ka Assyria.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kumne ong uta u syiem, ‘Wat shah ba u Hesekaïah un shukor ïa phi; naba un ym lah ban pyllait ïa phi na ka kti jong u:’",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> lymne wat ai ba u Hesekaïah un pynshaniah ïa phi ha U Trai, da kaba ong, ‘U Trai da shisha un pyllait ïa ngi, bad ïa kane ka shnong yn ym ai ha ka kti u syiem ka Assyria.’",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Wat sngap ïa u Hesekaïah: naba kumne ong u syiem ka Assyria, ‘To pynlong ka jingïasuk bad nga, bad to wan mih sha nga bad to u briew baroh un bam na la u dieng Waiñ, bad u briew baroh na la u dieng Dumbur, bad to dih u briew baroh na ki um la ka jong ka pukri;",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> haduh ba ngan wan bad shim noh ïa phi sha ka ri kum ka ri jong phi hi, ka ri u Kew bad ka Waiñ, ka ri u kpu bad ki brisoh, ka ri umphniang Olib bad ka ngap, ba phin ïoh im, bad ban ym ïap: bad wat sngap ïa u Hesekaïah, haba un pynkohnguh ïa phi, da kaba ong, U Trai un pyllait ïa ngi.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> La don kino kino ki blei jong ki jaid bynriew kiba mynno mynno ruh kiba la ju pyllait ïa la ka ri na ka kti u syiem ka Assyria?",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Hangno ki blei ka Hamath, bad ki jong ka Arpad? hangno ki blei jong ki Sepharbaim, jong ka Hena, bad jong ka Ibah? hato kita ki la pyllait ïa ka Samaria na ka kti jong nga?",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Kiei long kita hapdeng ki blei jong ki ri baroh, kiba la pyllait ïa la ka ri na ka kti jong nga, ba U Trai un pyllait ïa ka Jerusalem na ka kti jong nga?’ ”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Hynrei, ki briew ki la shu sngap jar, bad kim shym ïathuh ha u shikyntien: naba ka hukum u syiem ka la long, u da ong, “Wat phai ktien ïa u.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ynda kumta, u Eliakim u khun u Hilkiah, uba halor ka ïing, bad u Shebnah u nongthoh, bad u Joah u khun u Asaph u nongthoh rekord, ki la wan ha u Hesekaïah bad la ki jaiñ ba la kad, bad ki la ïathuh ha u ïa ki ktien u Rabshakeh."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ynda u syiem Hesekaïah u la ïohsngew ïa kata, u la kad ïa la ki jaiñ, bad u la kup ïa lade da ka jaiñ byrni, bad u la leit sha ïing U Trai.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la phah ïa u Eliakim, uba halor ka ïing, bad ïa u Shebnah u nongthoh, bad ïa ki rangbah jong ki lyngdoh, ba la kup da ki jaiñ byrni, sha u Isaïah u nongïathuhlypa u khun u Amos.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ki la ong ha u, “Kumne u ong u Hesekaïah, ‘Kane ka sngi ka long ka sngi ka jingjynjar, bad ka jingsympat, bad ka jingkrenbeiñ: naba ki khun ki la poi sha kaba kha, hynrei, ym don ka bor ban kha.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Lehse U Trai U Blei jong me un sngew ïa ki ktien u Rabshakeh baroh, uba u syiem ka Assyria u kynrad jong u, u la phah ban krenbeiñ ïa U Blei u ba-im, bad un sneng ïa kita ki ktien kiba U Trai U Blei jong me u la ïohsngew: namar kata, to pynkyntiew noh ïa la ka jingduwai na ka bynta kita kiba dang sah ïa kiba la iehnoh.’ ”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kumta, ki shakri u syiem Hesekaïah ki la wan ha u Isaïah.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u Isaïah u la ong ha ki, “Kumne phin ong ha u kynrad jong phi, ‘Kumne u ong U Trai, Wat sheptieng ïa kita ki ktien kiba me la ïohsngew, da kiba ki shakri u syiem ka Assyria ki la krenbeiñ ïa nga.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ha khmih, ngan buh mynsiem hapoh jong u, bad un ïohsngew ka jingbna, bad un leit phai sha la ka jong ka ri; bad ngan pynkyllon ïa u da ka waitlam ha la ka ri.’ ”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kumta, u Rabshakeh u la leit phai, bad u la shem ïa u syiem ka Assyria ba u ïaleh thma ïa ka Libnah: naba u la lah ïohsngew ba u la lah leit noh na Lakhish.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ynda u la ïohsngew ba ïalap shaphang u Tirhakah u syiem ka Ethiopia, “Ha khmih, u la wan ban ïaleh thma ïa me:” u la phah nonglam-ktien pat sha u Hesekaïah, u da ong,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Kumne phin kren ha u Hesekaïah u syiem ka Judah, da kaba ong, ‘Wat ai ba U Blei jong me ha uba me shaniah un shukor ïa me, da kaba ong, “Ïa ka Jerusalem yn ym ai ha ka kti u syiem ka Assyria.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ha khmih, me la ïohsngew kaei ba ki syiem ka Assyria ki la leh ha ki ri baroh, da kaba pynduh khoit ïa ki: ma me te men ïohlait?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hato ki blei jong ki jaid bynriew ki la pyllait ïa ki, ïa kiba ki kpa jong nga ki la pynduh, ka Gosan, bad ka Haran, bad ka Reseph, bad ki khun ka Eden, kiba la don ha Thelasar?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hangno u syiem ka Hamath, bad u syiem ka Arpad, bad u syiem ka shnong Sepharbaim, jong ka Hena, bad ka Ibah?’ ”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te haba u Hesekaïah u la ïoh diang kata ka shithi na ki nonglam-ktien u la pule ïa ka: te u Hesekaïah u la leit kiew sha ïing U Trai, bad u la plied ïa ka ha khmat U Trai.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u Hesekaïah u la duwai ha khmat U Trai, bad u la ong, “A Trai, U Blei ki Israel, uba shong halor ki Kherub, me tang ma me hi me long U Blei ka hima ka khyndew baroh; me la thaw ïa ka bneng bad ka khyndew.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> To pyndem ïa la ka shkor, A Trai, bad to sngew; peit ïa la ki khmat, A Trai, bad to khmih: bad to sngew ïa ki ktien u Sennakherib, da kiba u la phah ïa u ban krenbeiñ ïa U Blei u ba-im.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Da shisha, ko Trai, ki syiem ka Assyria ki la pynjot ïa ki jaid bynriew bad ki ri jong ki,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad ki la bred ïa ki blei jong ki ha ka ding: naba kim long ki blei, hynrei, ka jingthaw ki kti ki briew, dieng bad maw; namar kata, ki la pynduh ïa ki.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Namar kata te, A Trai U Blei jong ngi, nga kyrpad ïa me, pyllait im ïa ngi na ka kti jong u, ba ki hima ka khyndew baroh kin ïoh tip ba me long U Trai U Blei, tang ma me hi keiñ.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ynda kumta, u Isaïah u khun u Amos u la phah ha u Hesekaïah, u da ong, “Kumne ong U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, ‘Namar ba me la duwai ha nga pyrshah ïa u Sennakherib u syiem ka Assyria, nga la shahshkor ïa me.’",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kane ka long kata ka ktien ba U Trai u la kren shaphang jong u: “Ka theisotti ka khun ka Seïon ka la ibeiñ bad ka la rkhiebeiñ ïa me; ka khun ka Jerusalem ka la kyrngah la ka khlieh ha me.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Ïano me la krenbeiñ bad me krenbeiñ blei? bad pyrshah ïano me la pynsarong la ka ktien bad me la khmied ïa la ki khmat sha jrong? ïa uta u Bakhuid jong u Israel keiñ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Da la ki nonglam-ktien me la krenbeiñ ïa U Trai, bad me la ong, ‘Da ka jingbun ki kali ïapom jong nga, nga la wan kiew sha kliar ki lum bah, haduh kaba shapoh eh u Lebanon; bad ngan khet ïa ki dieng Kedar bajrong jong u, bad ïa ki dieng Kseh babha eh jong u: bad ngan leit rung shapoh ka jaka shong ba jngai tam jong u, ka khlaw ka lyngkha sei soh jong u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Nga la tih bad nga la dih ki um baphylla, bad da ki poh'jat jong nga, ngan pynrngad ïa ki wah ka Ijipt baroh.’",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> “Mem shym ïohsngew kumno nga la leh ïa ka la mynslem eh, bad nga la pynlong ïa ka naduh mynbarim? mynta te nga la pynjia ïa ka, ba men long khnang ïa ka ban pynduh ïa ki shnong ba la ker kut kum ki kynton bajot.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Namar kata, ki trai-shnong jong ki, ki la rit bor, ki la sheptieng bad ki la lyngngoh; ki la long kum u phlang ka lyngkha, bad kum u 'hur jyrngam, kum u phlang halor ki tnum ïing bad kum u Kew ba la ïapstai haba um pat san.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> “Hynrei, nga tip ïa kaba me shong, bad ïa kaba me leit, bad ïa kaba me wan, bad ïa kaba me bitar pyrshah ïa nga.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Namar kaba me bitar pyrshah ïa nga, bad namar ba ka jingleh sarong jong me ka la wan kiew sha ki shkor jong nga, namar kata, ngan buh ïa u khwai jong nga ha ka khmut jong me, bad ïa u lakam jong nga ha ki rmiang shyntur jong me, bad ngan pynphai pat ïa me da ka lynti na kaba me la wan.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Te kane kan long ka dak ïa me: ha kane ka snem phin bam ïa kata kaba shu mih hi, bad ha ka snem ka ba-ar na kaba mih na kata; te ha ka snem ka balai phin bet, bad ot, bad phin thung ki brisoh, bad bam ïa u soh jong ki.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad kita kiba la lait na ïing Judah, kita kiba dang sah, kin suhthied arsut, bad kin sei soh artet.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Naba na Jerusalem kin mih noh kita kiba dang sah, bad na u lum Seïon kita ki ban lait: ka jingshitrhem jong U Trai kan leh ïa kane.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> “Namar kata, kumne ong U Trai shaphang u syiem ka Assyria, ‘Un ym wan sha kane ka shnong, lymne siat uwei u khnam hangta, lymne un ym wan ha khmat jong ka da ka stieh, lymne tei kynton pyrshah ïa ka.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na ka lynti ba u la wan, na kajuh hi un leit phai pat, bad un ym wan sha kane ka shnong,’ ” ong U Trai.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> “Naba ngan ïada ïa kane ka shnong ban pynim ïa ka, na ka bynta jong nga hi, bad na ka bynta u Dabid u shakri jong nga.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Te ha kata ka miet, u angel U Trai u la mih noh, bad u la shoh ïap ha ka dara ki Assyria shispah phraphew san hajar ngut: te ynda ki briew ki la khie dang step ha kaba lashai, ha khmih, ki la long ki metïap baroh.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Kumta u Sennakherib u syiem ka Assyria u la leit noh, bad ynda u la leit phai pat, u la shong ha Ninebeh.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te haba u dang mane ha ka ïing u Nisrok u blei jong u, u Adrammelek bad u Shareser ki la pom ïap ïa u da ka waitlam: bad ki la phet ïap sha ka ri Ararat. Bad u Esarhaddon u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ha kita ki sngi, u Hesekaïah u la pang ïa ka ban ïap noh. Te u Isaïah u nongïathuhlypa u khun u Amos u la wan ha u, bad u la ong ha u, “Kumne u ong U Trai, To pynbeit ïa la ka ïing; naba men ïap, bad men ym im.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ynda kumta, u la phai ïa la ka khmat sha ka kynroh, bad u la duwai ha U Trai, u da ong.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to kynmaw mynta, A Trai, kumno nga la ïaid ha khmat jong me ha ka jingshisha bad da ka dohnud ka bajanai, bad nga la leh ïa kata ka babha ha khmat jong me.” Te u Hesekaïah u la ïam eh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te shuwa ba u Isaïah um pat lap ba mih noh napdeng ka shnong, ka ktien U Trai ka la wan ha u, kaba ong,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “To phai pat, bad to ong ha u Hesekaïah u rangbah u paidbah jong nga, ‘Kumne ong U Trai, U Blei u Dabid u kpa jong me, Nga la shahshkor ïa ka jingduwai jong me, nga la ïohi ïa ki ummat jong me: ha khmih, ngan pynkhiah ïa me: ha ka sngi ka balai men leit kiew sha ka ïing U Trai.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad ngan pyntam shuh ïa ki sngi jong me sa khatsan snem: bad ngan pyllait ïa me bad ïa kane ka shnong na ka kti u syiem ka Assyria; bad ngan da ïa kane ka shnong na ka bynta jong nga hi, bad na ka bynta u Dabid u shakri jong nga.’ ”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u Isaïah u la ong, “To shim 'pu soh Dumbur uwei. Te haba ki la shim ki la sop ha kata kaba thung, bad u la koit.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u Hesekaïah u la ong ha u Isaïah, “Kaei kan long ka dak ba U Trai un pynkhiah ïa nga, bad ba ngan leit kiew sha ka ïing U Trai ha ka sngi ka balai?”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u Isaïah u la ong, “Kane kan long ka dak ha me na U Trai, ba U Trai un leh ïa kane kaba u la kren: ka syrngiew kan leit sha khmat shiphew kyrdan, ne kan kynran shadien shiphew kyrdan?”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U Hesekaïah te u la ïathuh, “Ka long kaba jem ïa ka syrngiew ban nang hiar shiphew kyrdan: em, hynrei, to ai ba ka syrngiew kan kynran da dien shiphew kyrdan.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u Isaïah u nongïathuhlypa u la pyrta ha U Trai: bad u la pynkynran da dien ïa kata ka syrngiew shiphew kyrdan, da kaba ka la lah hiar ha ki kyrdan u Ahas.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ha kata ka por, u Berodak-baladan u khun u Baladan, u syiem ka Babilon, u la phah ïa ki shithi bad ki jingai sngewbha ha u Hesekaïah: naba u la lah bna ba u Hesekaïah u la lah pang.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Hesekaïah u la shahshkor ïa ki, bad u la pyni ha ki, ïa ka ïing, kiei kiei kiba kordor ki jong u baroh, ïa ka rupa, bad ka ksiar, bad ki jingiwbih, bad ka umphniang bakordor, bad ka ïing buh atiar jong u, bad ïa kiei kiei baroh ba la shem ha ki jingkynshew jong u: ym shym la don kaei kaei ha ka ïing jong u, lymne ha ka hima jong u baroh, ba u Hesekaïah um shym la pyni ha ki.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ynda kumta, u nongïathuhlypa Isaïah u la wan ha u syiem Hesekaïah, bad u la ong ha u, “Kine ki briew ki la ong aïu? Bad na-ei ki la wan poi sha me?” Bad u Hesekaïah u la ong, “Ki la wan poi na ka ri kaba jngai, naduh Babilon keiñ.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u la ong, “Ki la ïohi aïu ha ka ïing jong me?” Te u Hesekaïah u la ïathuh, “Baroh kat kiba ha ka ïing jong nga ki la ïohi: ym don kaei kaei hapdeng ki jingkynshew jong nga ba ngam shym la pyni ha ki.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te u Isaïah u la ong ha u Hesekaïah, “To sngew ïa ka ktien U Trai.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> ‘Ha khmih, ki sngi kin jia, ba baroh kaba don ha ka ïing jong me, bad ïa kata kaba ki kpa jong me ki la kynshew haduh kane ka sngi, yn kit noh sha Babilon: ym don kaei kaei ka ban sah,’ ong U Trai.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> ‘Bad na ki khun shynrang jong me ki ban sa mih na me, kiba men sa pynkha, kin leit lam noh: bad kin long ki ïunukh ha ka ïingsyiem u syiem ka Babilon.’ ”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ynda kumta, u Hesekaïah u la ong ha u Isaïah, “Ka babha ka long ka ktien U Trai kaba me la kren.” U la ong ruh, “Ym long kumta, lada ka jingsuk bad ka jingshisha kin long ha ki sngi jong nga?”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Hesekaïah, bad ka bor jong u baroh, bad kumno u la pynlong ïa kata ka nan, bad kata ka lynti um, bad u la pynpoi ïa ka um shapoh ka shnong, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ka Judah?",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u Hesekaïah u la thiah bad la ki kpa: bad u Manasseh u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> U Manasseh u la long khat-ar snem ka rta mynba u la sdang ban synshar: bad u la synshar sanphew san snem ha Jerusalem: bad ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka la long “ka Hephsibah.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai, kat kum ki jingijli kita ki Jentil, kiba U Trai u la beh noh ha khmat ki khun Israel.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Naba u la tei pat ïa kita ki jaka bajrong kiba u Hesekaïah u kpa jong u, u la pynduh; bad u la pynïeng ïa ki duwan ïa u Baal, bad u la pynlong ïa ki Asherah, kumba la leh u Ahab u syiem ki Israel, bad u la mane ïa u paidbah bneng baroh, bad u la shakri ïa ki.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u la tei ruh ïa ki duwan ha ïing U Trai, shaphang kaba U Trai u la ong, “Ha Jerusalem ngan buh ïa la ka kyrteng.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u la tei ki duwan ïa u paidbah bneng baroh ha ki ar tylli ki phyllaw ki jong U Trai.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u la pynïaid ïa la u khun lyngba ka ding, u la khan ïa ki por, bad u la kren byrtong, bad u la leit ha kita kiba kren blei, bad ha kita kiba kren byrtong: u la leh ka basniew shikatdei ha khmat U Trai, ban pankwah ïa u ban bitar.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u la pynïeng ruh ïa ka dur bleithaw ka Asherah, kaba u la thaw, ha kata ka ïing shaphang kaba U Trai u la ong ha u Dabid bad ha u Solomon u khun jong u, “Ha kane ka ïing, bad ha Jerusalem, ïa kaba nga la jied na ki jaid Israel baroh, ngan buh ïa la ka kyrteng ha la ka rta:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> lymne ngan ym pynïaid sakma shuh ïa ki kjat ki Israel na kata ka ri kaba nga la ai ha ki kpa jong ki; lada kin tang sumar ban leh kat kum kita baroh ba nga la hukum ïa ki, bad kat kum kata baroh ka hukum kaba u Moses u shakri jong nga u la hukum ïa ki.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hynrei, kim shahshkor: bad u Manasseh u la pynshoi ïa ki ban leh ïa kata ka basniew kham tam ïa kaba la leh kita ki jaid bynriew, kiba U Trai u la pynduh ha khmat ki khun Israel.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te U Trai u la kren da ki shakri jong u ki nongïathuhlypa, u da ong,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Namar ba u Manasseh u syiem ka Judah u la leh ïa kine ki jingijli, bad u la leh bymman palat ïa kata baroh ba la leh ki Amor, kiba la mynshuwa jong u, bad u la pynlong ïa ki Judah ruh ban leh pop da ki bleithaw jong u:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> namar kata, kumne ong U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, ‘Ha khmih, nga pynhap kum kata ka basniew halor ka Jerusalem bad ka Judah, ba jar uba ïohsngew ïa ka, un kyllut ki shkor jong u baroh ar.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ngan thew halor ka Jerusalem da u ksai jong ka Samaria, bad da u sawar ka ïing u Ahab: bad ngan sait ïa ka Jerusalem kumba u briew u sait ïa ka pliang, u sait, u da pyndem pyllup ïa ka.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ngan bred noh ïa kaba dang sah na ka ri kynti jong nga, bad ngan ai noh ïa ki ha ka kti ki nongshun jong ki: bad kin jia long ka jingïaknieh bad ka jinglute ha ki nongshun jong ki baroh;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> namar ba ki la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat jong nga, bad ki la pankwah ïa nga ban bitar, naduh kata ka sngi ba ki kpa jong ki, ki la mih noh na ka ri Ijipt, haduh kane ka sngi keiñ.’ ”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u Manasseh u la pynmih ruh shikatdei ka snam balui lui, haduh ba u la pynshlei ïa ka Jerusalem nadong shadong; nalor kata ka pop jong u da kaba u la pynlong ïa ka Judah ban leh pop, ha kaba leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Manasseh, bad baroh kaba u la leh, bad ïa ka pop jong u ïa kaba u la leh pop, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ka Judah?",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u Manasseh u la thiah bad la ki kpa, bad la tep ïa u ha ka kper ka ïing jong u hi, ha ka kper u Ussa keiñ: bad u Amon u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> U Amon u la long arphew ar snem ka rta mynba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar ar snem ha Jerusalem: bad ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka la long “ka Meshullemeth” ka khun u Harus kaba na Jotbah.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai, kumba la leh u Manasseh u kpa jong u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te u la ïaid ha kata ka lynti baroh kaba u kpa jong u, u la ïaid, bad u la shakri ïa ki blei kiba u kpa jong u, u la shakri, bad u la mane ïa ki:",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> bad u la lyndet ïa U Trai, U Blei ki kpa jong u, bad um shym ïaid shuh ha ka lynti U Trai.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ki shakri u Amon ki la ïashet ïa u, bad ki la pynïap ïa u syiem ha ka ïing jong u hi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Hynrei, ki briew jong ka ri ki la ïa-pynïap ïa kita baroh kiba la ïashet ïa u syiem Amon; bad ki briew jong ka ri ki la pynlong syiem ïa u Josaïah u khun jong u ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Amon kiba u la leh, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ka Judah?",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad la tep ïa u ha ka jingtep jong u ha ka kper u Ussa: bad u Josaïah u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> U Josaïah u la long phra snem ka rta mynba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar laiphew wei snem ha Jerusalem: bad ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka la long “ka Jedidah” ka khun u Adaïah kaba na Boskath.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u la leh ïa kata ka babha ha khmat U Trai, bad u la ïaid ha baroh ka lynti jong u Dabid u kpa jong u, bad um shym phai bakla sha kamon lane sha kadiang.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te ha ka bakhatphra snem jong u syiem Josaïah, u syiem u la phah ïa u Shaphan u khun u Asaliah, u khun u Meshullam, u nongthoh, sha ka ïing U Trai, u da ong,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Khie leit kiew sha u Hilkiah u rangbah lyngdoh, ba un kheiñ ïa u sbai ba la wallam sha ka ïing U Trai, ïa uba ki nongap jingkhang ki la ïalum na ki paidbah:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad to kin ai noh ïa u ha ka kti ki nongtrei kiba khmih ïa ka ïing U Trai: bad to kita kin aiti ïa u ha ki nongtrei kiba don ha ka ïing U Trai, ba kin shna pat ïa ki jingpra jong ka ïing;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> ha ki misteri, bad ha ki nongtei kynroh, bad ha ki nongshtah maw; bad ban thied ki dieng bad ki maw ba la shniah ban shna pat ïa ki ïing.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hynrei, ym shym la pynlong jingïakheiñ ei ei bad ki shaphang uta u sbai ba la ai ha ka kti jong ki; naba ki la leh hok.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u Hilkiah u rangbah lyngdoh u la ong ha u Shaphan u nongthoh, “Nga la shem ïa Ka Kitab Ka Hukum ha ka ïing U Trai.” Bad u Hilkiah u la aiti ïa kata Ka Kitab ha u Shaphan, u te u la pule ïa ka.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Shaphan u nongthoh u la wan ha u syiem, bad u la wallam ktien pat ha u syiem, bad u la ong, “Ki shakri jong me ki la shim noh ïa uta u sbai ba la shem ha ka ïing, bad ki la ai noh ïa u ha ka kti ki nongtrei kiba khmih ïa ka ïing U Trai.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u Shaphan u nongthoh u la ïathuh ha u syiem, u da ong, “U Hilkiah lyngdoh u la ai ha nga Ka Kitab.” Bad u Shaphan u la pule ïa ka ha khmat u syiem.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ynda u syiem u la ïohsngew ïa ki ktien Ka Kitab Ka Hukum, u la kad ïa la ki jaiñ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u syiem u la hukum ïa u Hilkiah lyngdoh, bad u Ahikam u khun u Shaphan, bad u Akhbor u khun u Mikaïah, bad u Shaphan u nongthoh, bad u Asahiah u shakri u syiem, u da ong,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Khie leit ïakylli ïa U Trai na ka bynta jong nga, bad na ka bynta u paidlang, bad na ka bynta ki Judah baroh, shaphang ki ktien jong kane Ka Kitab ba la shem: namar kaba khraw ka jingbitar U Trai kaba la meh pyrshah ïa ngi, namar ki kpa jong sngi kim shym la shahshkor ïa ki ktien kane Ka Kitab, ban leh katba kum kata baroh ba la thoh shaphang jong ngi.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kumta, u Hilkiah lyngdoh, bad u Ahikam, bad u Akhbor, bad u Shaphan, bad u Asahiah, ki la leit ha ka Huldah ka nongïathuhlypa, ka tnga u Shallum u khun u Tikbah, u khun u Harhas, u nongsumar ki jaiñ; (ka te ka la shong ha Jerusalem ha Mishneh;) bad ki la ïakren bad ka.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ka la ïathuh ha ki, “Kumne ong U Trai, U Blei ki Israel: ‘To ïathuh phi ha uta u briew uba la phah ïa phi ha nga.’",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kumne ong U Trai, ‘Ha khmih, ngan wallam ïa ka basniew halor kane ka jaka, bad halor ki nongshong jong ka, baroh ki ktien jong Ka Kitab keiñ kaba u syiem ka Judah u la pule:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> namar ki la lyndet ïa nga, bad ki la thang ka jingiwbih ha kiwei pat ki blei, ba kin ïoh pynbitar ïa nga da ka kam ki kti jong ki baroh; namar kata, ka jingbitar jong nga kan meh pyrshah ïa kane ka jaka, bad yn ym pynlip ïa ka.’ ”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hynrei, ha u syiem ka Judah, uba la phah ïa phi ban ïakylli ïa U Trai, kumne phin ong ha u, “Kumne u ong U Trai, U Blei ki Israel: ‘Shaphang kita ki ktien kiba me la ïohsngew,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> namar ba ka dohnud jong me kaba jem, bad me la pynrit ïa lade ha khmat U Trai, ynda me la ïohsngew ïa kaba nga la kren pyrshah ïa kane ka jaka, bad pyrshah ïa ki nongshong jong ka, ba kin sa jia long ka jingkynjah bad ka jingtim, bad me la kad ïa la ki jaiñ, bad me la ïam ha khmat jong nga: nga ruh nga la ïohsngew ïa me,’ ” ong U Trai.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Namar kata, ha khmih, ngan ïalum ïa me sha ki kpa jong me, bad yn ïalum ïa me sha ka jingtep ha kaba suk, lymne ki khmat jong me kin ym ïohi ïa kata ka basniew kaba ngan wallam halor kane ka jaka.” Te ki la wallam ktien pat ha u syiem."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u syiem u la phah, bad u la ïalum ha u ïa ki tymmen basan baroh jong ka Judah bad jong ka Jerusalem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u syiem u la leit kiew sha ka ïing U Trai, bad ki rangbah Judah baroh bad ki Jerusalem baroh lem bad u, bad ki lyngdoh, bad ki nongïathuhlypa, bad ki paidbah baroh, ki barit bad ki bakhraw: bad u la pule ha ki shkor jong ki, ïa ki ktien jong Ka Kitab Ka Jutang baroh ïa kaba la shem ha ka ïing U Trai.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u syiem, u la ïeng hajan u païa, bad u la pynlong ïa ka jutang ha khmat U Trai, ban ïaid nadien U Trai, bad ban sumar ïa ki hukum jong U, bad ki jingphla jong U, bad ki aiñ jong U, da ka dohnud jong u baroh, bad da ka mynsiem jong u baroh, ïa ka ban pynskhem ïa ki ktien jong kane ka jutang kiba la thoh ha kane Ka Kitab: bad ki paidbah baroh ki la ïeng ha kata ka jutang.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te u syiem u la hukum ïa u Hilkiah u rangbah lyngdoh, bad ïa ki lyngdoh kiba kham hapoh, bad ïa ki nongsumar ka jingkhang, ba kin pynmih noh na ka templ jong U Trai ïa ki pliang baroh ïa kiba la thaw ïa u Baal, bad ïa ka Asherah, bad ïa u paidbah ka bneng baroh: bad u la thang ïa ki shabar ka Jerusalem ha ki lyngkha Kidron, bad u la kit ïa ka dpei jong ki sha Bethel.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u la pynduh ïa kita ki lyngdoh bleithaw, ïa kiba ki syiem ka Judah ki la lah thung ban thang ka jingiwbih ha ki jaka bajrong ha ki shnong Judah, bad ha ki jaka baroh sawdong ka Jerusalem; ïa kita ruh kiba thang jingiwbih ïa u Baal, ïa ka sngi, bad ïa u bnai, bad ïa ki planet, bad ïa u paidbah bneng baroh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u la pynmih noh ïa ka Asherah na ka ïing U Trai, shabar ka Jerusalem, haduh ka wah Kidron, bad u la thang ïa ka ha ka wah Kidron, bad u la pynlwet bin bin ïa ka, bad u la khalah ïa kata kaba lwet halor ki jingtep ki briew bapoh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u la pynkyllon ïa ki ïing ki kynja Sodom, kiba la don ha ka ïing U Trai, ha kiba ki kynthei ki ju thain ki pyrda ïa ka Asherah.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u la pynmih ïa ki lyngdoh baroh na ki shnong Judah, bad u la pynsang naduh Geba haduh Beer-sheba, ïa kita ki jaka bajrong ha kiba ki lyngdoh ki la ju thang jingiwbih; bad u la pynkyllon ïa kita ki jaka bajrong jong ki jingkhang kiba ha kaba rung ha ka khyrdop u Joshua u nongsynshar ka shnong, kiba la don sha ka kti kadiang u briew ha ka khyrdop ka shnong.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hynrei, pynban, ki lyngdoh ki jaka bajrong kim shym wan kiew sha ka duwan U Trai ha Jerusalem, hynrei, ki la bam u 'pu khlem thiat hapdeng ki paralok jong ki.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u la pynsang ïa ka Tophet, kaba ha ka them ki khun u Hinnom, ba ym don ba lah ban pynïaid ïa la u khun lane ka khun lyngba ka ding ïa u Molek.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u la pynkynriah noh ïa kita ki kulai ïa kiba ki syiem ka Judah ki la lah ai ïa ka sngi, ha kaba rung sha ka ïing U Trai, hajan ka kamra u Nathan-melek u ïunukh, kaba la don hapoh kut; bad u la thang ïa ki kali jong ka sngi da ka ding.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ïa ki duwan kiba la don halor jrong ka kamra u Ahas kaba kham haneng, ïa kiba ki syiem ka Judah ki la thaw, bad ïa ki duwan kiba u Manasseh u la thaw ha ki ar tylli ki phyllaw ka ïing U Trai, ïa kita u syiem u la pynkyllon khram, bad u la shoh pynlwet ïa ki nangta, bad u la phah bred ïa ka synrum jong ki sha ka wah duid Kidron.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ïa ki jaka bajrong kiba ha khmat ka Jerusalem, kiba sha kamon u lum ka jingtngit, kiba u Solomon u syiem ki Israel u la lah tei ïa ka Ashtoreth ka jingijli ki nong Sidon, bad ïa u Khemosh ka jingijli ki Moab, bad ïa u Milkom ka jingijli ki khun u Ammon, ïa kita u syiem u la pynsang.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u la pynlwet lyngkhot lyngkhai ïa ki mawblei, bad u la khet noh ïa ki Asherah, bad u la pyndap ïa ki jaka jong ki ruh da ki shyieng ki briew.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ïa kata ka duwan ruh kaba ha Bethel, bad ïa ka jaka bajrong kaba u la tei u Jeroboam u khun u Nebat, uba la pynlong ïa ki Israel ban leh pop, ïa kata ka duwan keiñ bad ïa kata ka jaka bajrong u la pynkyllon; bad u la thang ïa kata ka jaka bajrong bad u la pynlwet bin bin ïa ka, u la thang ïa kata ka Asherah ruh de.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te haba u Josaïah u la kyrtiang, u la ïohi ïa ki jingtep kiba la don hangta ha uta u lum; te haba u la phah shim ïa ki shyieng na kita ki jingtep, u la thang ïa ki halor ka duwan, bad u la pynsang ïa ka, katba kum ka ktien U Trai ïa kaba u briew jong U Blei u la pynbna, uba la pynbna ïa kine kiei kiei.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ynda kumta, u la ong, “Ka jingtei aïu katai kaba nga ïohi?” Te ki rangbah kata ka shnong ki la ïathuh ha u, “Ka long ka jingtep u briew jong U Blei, uba la wan ha Judah, bad uba la pynbna ïa kine kiei kiei kiba me la leh ïa ka duwan ka Bethel.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u la ong, “To ieh ïa u; wat shah ïa uno uno ban pynkynriah ïa ki shyieng jong u.” Kumta, ki la iehnoh noh ïa ki shyieng jong u, lem bad ki shyieng uta u nongïathuhlypa uba la wan na Samaria.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ïa baroh ki ïing ruh jong ki jaka bajrong kiba la don ha ki shnong Samaria, ïa kiba ki syiem ki Israel ki la lah tei ban pankwah ïa U Trai ban bitar, u Josaïah u la pynduh noh, bad u la leh ïa ki katba kum kita ki kam baroh kiba u la lah leh ha Bethel.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ïa ki lyngdoh baroh jong ki jaka bajrong kiba la don hangta u la pynïap, halor kita ki duwan, bad u la thang ïa ki shyieng briew halor jong ki; bad u la leit phai sha Jerusalem.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te u syiem u la hukum ïa ki briew baroh u da ong, “To rakhe ïa Ka Niam Ka Jinglait ha U Trai U Blei jong phi, kat kumba la thoh ha kane Ka Kitab Ka Jutang.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Shisha ym pat ju rakhe kat kata Ka Jinglait naduh ki sngi ki nongbishar kiba la bishar ïa ki Israel, lymne ha baroh ki sngi ki syiem ki Israel, lymne ha jong ki syiem ka Judah;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> hynrei, ha ka snem khatphra jong u syiem Josaïah la rakhe ïa kane Ka Jinglait ha U Trai ha Jerusalem.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ïa kita ruh kiba shong ksuid, bad ïa kiba kren byrtong, bad ïa ki teraph, bad ïa ki dur bleithaw, bad ïa ki jingijli baroh katba la shem ha ka ri Judah bad ha Jerusalem, u Josaïah u la pynduh noh, ba un ïoh pynskhem ïa ki ktien jong kata ka hukum kiba la thoh ha kata Ka Kitab ba u Hilkiah lyngdoh u la shem ha ka ïing U Trai.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te ha shuwa jong u, ym shym la don syiem kum ma u, uba la phai sha U Trai da ka dohnud baroh, bad da la ka mynsiem baroh, bad da la ka bor baroh, katba kum ka hukum u Moses baroh; lymne ym shym la mih hadien jong u uba kum ma u.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> La kumta ruh, U Trai um shym phai noh na ka jingotshla ka jingbitar bakhraw jong u, da kaba ka jingbitar jong u ka la meh pyrshah ïa ka Judah, na ka bynta kita ki jingpankwah baroh da kiba u Manasseh u la pankwah ïa u.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te U Trai u la ong, “Ngan pynkynriah noh ïa ka Judah ruh na khmat jong nga, kumba nga la pynkynriah noh ïa ki Israel, bad ngan kyntait noh ïa kane ka shnong kaba nga la jied, ïa ka Jerusalem keiñ, bad ïa ka ïing shaphang kaba nga la ong, ‘Ka kyrteng jong nga kan long hangta.’ ”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Josaïah, bad baroh kiba u la leh, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ka Judah?",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ha ki sngi jong u, u Pharaoh-nekoh u syiem ka ri Ijipt u la leit kiew ban ïaleh ïa u syiem ka Assyria ha ka wah Ïuphratis: bad u syiem Josaïah u la mih ban ïaleh ïa u; te ynda u la lah ïohi ïa u, u la pynïap ïa u ha Megiddo.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ki shakri jong u te, ki la leit kit ïap ïa u ha ka kali na Megiddo, bad haba ki la wallam ïa u sha Jerusalem, ki la tep ïa u ha ka jingtep jong u hi. Te ki briew jong ka ri, ki la shim ïa u Jehoahas u khun u Josaïah, bad ki la pynsleh ïa u, bad ki la thung syiem ïa u ha ka jaka u kpa jong u.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> U Jehoahas u la long arphew lai snem ka rta mynba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar lai bnai ha Jerusalem: bad ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka la long “ka Hamutal” ka khun u Jeremaïah na Libnah.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai, katba kum kata baroh ba ki kpa jong u ki la lah leh.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te u Pharaoh-nekoh u la khum ïa u ha Riblah ha ka ri Hamath, ba un ym ïoh synshar ha Jerusalem; bad u la khrong ïa ka ri shispah ki talent rupa, bad shi talent ksiar.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad u Pharaoh-nekoh u la pynlong syiem ïa u Eliakim u khun u Josaïah ha ka jaka u Josaïah u kpa jong u, bad u la pynkylla ïa ka kyrteng jong u, “u Jehoïakim”: hynrei, u la shim noh ïa u Jehoahas; bad ynda u la poi sha ka ri Ijipt, u la ïap hangta.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Te u Jehoïakim u la ai ha u Pharaoh ïa kata ka rupa bad ïa kata ka ksiar; hynrei, u la khrong ïa ka ri ïa ka ban ai ïa uta u sbai katba kum ka hukum u Pharaoh: u la khrong ïa kata ka rupa bad ka ksiar na ki briew jong ka ri, man la u briew kat kum ka khrong ba dei ïa u, ïa ka ban ai ïa ka ha u Pharaoh-nekoh.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> U Jehoïakim u la long arphew san snem ka rta mynba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar khatwei snem ha Jerusalem: te ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka la long “ka Sebidah” ka khun u Pedaïah uba na Rumah.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Bad u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai, kat kum kata baroh ba ki kpa jong u ki la lah leh."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ha ki sngi jong u, u Nebukhadnessar u syiem ka Babilon u la wan kiew, bad u Jehoïakim u la wan long u shakri ïa u lai snem: hadien kata, u la kylla bad u la ïaleh bad u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad U Trai u la phah ïaleh ïa u da ki kynhun ki Khaldi, bad ki kynhun ki Syria, bad ki kynhun ki Moab, bad ki kynhun ki khun u Ammon, bad u la phah ïa ki ban ïaleh ïa ka Judah ïa ka ban pynjot ïa ka, katba kum ka ktien U Trai, kaba u la kren da ka kti ki shakri jong u ki nongïathuhlypa.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Shisha da ka hukum U Trai kane ka la jia ha ki Judah, ïa ka ban pynkynriah noh ïa ki na khmat jong u, na ka bynta ki pop u Manasseh, kat kum kata baroh kaba u la leh;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> bad na ka bynta ka snam balui lui ruh kaba u la pynmih; naba u la pynshlei ïa ka Jerusalem da ka snam balui lui: te U Trai um map shuh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Jehoïakim, bad baroh kaba u la leh, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ka Judah?",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kumta u Jehoïakim u la thiah bad la ki kpa; bad u Jehoïakhin u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u syiem ka ri Ijipt um shym la wan mih shuh na la ka ri: naba u syiem ka Babilon u la lah knieh noh baroh phar kaba la dei ka jong u syiem ka Ijipt, naduh ka wah Ijipt haduh ka wah Ïuphratis.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U Jehoïakhin u la long khatphra snem ka rta mynba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar ha Jerusalem lai bnai: bad ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka la long “ka Nehushta” ka khun u Elnathan uba na Jerusalem.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai, kat kum kata baroh ba u kpa jong u, u la lah leh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ha kata ka por, ki shakri u Nebukhadnessar u syiem ka Babilon ki la wan kiew sha Jerusalem, bad ïa ka shnong la ker kut.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u Nebukhadnessar u syiem ka Babilon u la wan poi sha ka shnong, katba ki shakri jong u ki la ïadang ker kut ïa ka.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u Jehoïakhin u syiem ka Judah u la leit mih noh sha u syiem ka Babilon, ma u, bad ka kmie jong u, bad ki shakri jong u, bad ki rangbah jong u, bad ki ïunukh jong u: bad u syiem ka Babilon u la kem ïa u ha ka snem ka baphra ka jingsynshar jong u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u la kit noh nangta ïa ki jingkynshew ka ïing U Trai baroh, bad ïa ki jingkynshew ka ïing u syiem, bad u la pynpait lyngkhot lyngkhai ïa ki pliang ksiar baroh kiba u Solomon u syiem ki Israel u la lah thaw ha ka templ U Trai, kumba U Trai u la lah ong.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u la ring mraw ïa ka Jerusalem baroh, bad ïa ki rangbah baroh, bad ïa ki riewkhlaiñ bashlur baroh, shiphew hajar ki mraw keiñ, bad ïa ki nongthaw jingthaw bad ki kamar baroh; ym don ba sah shuh, sa tang ki baduk tam na ki briew ka ri.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u la ring noh ïa u Jehoïakhin sha Babilon; bad ïa ka kmie u syiem, bad ki tnga u syiem, bad ki ïunukh jong u, bad ki rangbah ka ri, u la ring mraw na Jerusalem sha Babilon.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ïa kiba khraw bor baroh, hynñiew hajar keiñ, bad ïa ki nongthaw jingthaw bad ki kamar shi hajar, kita baroh kiba khlaiñ bad kiba bit ïa ka thma, ïa kita keiñ u syiem ka Babilon u la ring mraw sha Babilon.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u syiem ka Babilon u la pynlong syiem ha ka jaka jong u ïa u Mathaniah u para u kpa jong u, bad u la pynkylla ïa ka kyrteng jong u, u Sedekaïah.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U Sedekaïah u la long arphew wei snem ka rta haba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar khatwei snem ha Jerusalem. Bad ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka la long “ka Hamutal” ka khun u Jeremaïah uba na Libnah.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai kat kum kata baroh ba u Jehoïakim u la leh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Naba da ka jingbitar U Trai ka la jia ha Jerusalem bad Judah, haduh ba u la lah bred ïa ki na khmat jong u. Bad u Sedekaïah u la ïaleh pyrshah ïa u syiem ka Babilon."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ka la jia ha ka snem ka bakhyndai ka jingsynshar jong u, ha u bnai u bashiphew, ha ka sngi ka bashiphew jong uta u bnai, ba u Nebukhadnessar u syiem ka Babilon u la wan poi, ma u bad u paidïapom jong u baroh, ban ïaleh ïa ka Jerusalem, bad u la sher dara pyrshah ïa ka; bad ki la tei ïa ki kut pyrshah ïa ka baroh sawdong.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kumta, ïa ka shnong la ker kut haduh ka snem ka bakhatwei u syiem Sedekaïah.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ha ka sngi ka bakhyndai jong u bnai u basaw, ka 'nemsniew ka la jur ha ka shnong, katba ym don kpu shuh ïa ki briew jong ka ri.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te la pynlong ka jingtwa ha ka shnong, bad baroh ki nongïapom ki la phet ïap mynmiet na ka lynti ka khyrdop hapdeng ki ar tylli ki kynroh, kaba hajan ka kper u syiem: (te ki Khaldi ki la don pyrshah ïa ka shnong baroh sawdong:) bad u syiem u la leit na ka lynti ka Arabah.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hynrei, u paidïapom ki Khaldi u la bud nadien u syiem, bad u la lap ïa u ha ka madan Jerikho: bad ïa u paidïapom jong u baroh la pynsaphred na u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la kem ïa u syiem, bad ki la leit lam ïa u ha u syiem ka Babilon ha Riblah; bad ki la bishar ïa u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ki la pynïap ïa ki khun u Sedekaïah ha khmat jong u, bad ïa ki khmat u Sedekaïah ki la khlaw noh, bad ki la khum ïa u da ki kynjri, bad ki la leit lam ïa u sha Babilon.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te ha u bnai u basan, ha ka sngi ka bahynñiew jong uta u bnai, kaba la long ka snem ka bakhatkhyndai jong u syiem Nebukhadnessar u syiem ka Babilon, u Nebusaradan u kaptan ka karod, u shakri u syiem ka Babilon, u la wan sha Jerusalem:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> bad u la thang ïa ka ïing U Trai, bad ïa ka ïing u syiem; bad baroh ki ïing ka Jerusalem, ka ïingbah baroh keiñ, u la thang da ka ding.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u paidïapom ki Khaldi baroh, uba don lem bad u kaptan ka karod, u la pyntwa ïa ki kynroh ka Jerusalem baroh sawdong.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki briew kiba la iehnoh ha ka shnong, bad kita kiba la hap noh, kiba la hap sha u syiem ka Babilon keiñ, bad kiba dang sah na u paidbah, ïa kita u Nebusaradan u kaptan ka karod u la ring mraw.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hynrei, u kaptan ka karod u la iehnoh ïa ki baduk tam jong ka ri ban long ki nongsumar bri bad ki nongrep.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ïa kita ki rishot rnong kiba la don ha ka ïing U Trai, bad ki jingpynshong bad ïa ka duriaw rnong kiba la don ha ïing U Trai, ki Khaldi ki la pynpait lyngkhot lyngkhai, bad ki la leit lam ïa ka rnong jong ki sha Babilon.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ïa ki khiew, bad ïa ki siang heh, bad ïa ki jinglur sharak, bad ïa ki siang, bad ïa ki khiew ki pliang rnong baroh da kiba ki kam jingkam, ki la kit noh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ïa ki pliang dieng, bad ïa ki pliang; kata kaba da ka ksiar, ha ka ksiar, bad kata kaba da ka rupa, ha ka rupa, u kaptan ka karod u la shim noh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kita ki ar tylli ki rishot, kata kawei ka duriaw, bad kita ki jingpynshong, ïa kiba u Solomon u la lah thaw ïa ka ïing U Trai; ka rnong jong kine ki pliang baroh ka la long khlem jingthew.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ka jingjrong uwei u rishot ka la long khatphra pruh, bad ka khlieh rnong halor jong u; te ka jingjrong kata ka khlieh ka la long lai pruh; bad ka jingthain jar bad ki soh Pong halor kata ka khlieh baroh sawdong, baroh da ka rnong; bad kum kine hi u rishot u ba-ar u la don lem bad ka jingthain jar.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u kaptan ka karod u la kem ïa u Seraïah u lyngdoh rangbah, bad ïa u Sephanaïah u lyngdoh u ba-ar, bad ïa lai ngut ki nongap ka jingkhang:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bad na ka shnong u la kem ïa u rangbah uba la thung halor ki nongïapom; bad san ngut na kita kiba ju ïohi ïa ka khmat u syiem, ïa kiba la shem ha ka shnong; bad ïa u nongthoh u kaptan u paidïapom, uba ïalum ïa ki briew jong ka ri; bad ïa ki hynriewphew ngut na ki briew jong ka ri, ïa kiba la shem ha ka shnong.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u Nebusaradan u kaptan ka karod u la kem ïa ki, bad u la leit lam ïa ki sha u syiem ka Babilon ha Riblah.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u syiem ka Babilon u la pom ïa ki, bad u la pynïap ïa ki ha Riblah ha ka ri Hamath. Kumta, ïa u Judah la ring mraw na ka ri jong u.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te shaphang kita ki briew ïa kiba la iehnoh ha ka ri Judah, ïa kiba u Nebukhadnessar u syiem ka Babilon u la iehnoh, halor kita keiñ u la thung nongsynshar ïa u Gedalaïah u khun u Ahikam, u khun u Shaphan.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te haba ki kaptan ki shipai baroh, ma ki bad ki briew jong ki, ki la ïohsngew ba u syiem ka Babilon u la lah thung nongsynshar ïa u Gedalaïah, ki la wan ha u Gedalaïah ha Mispah, u Ishmael keiñ u khun u Nethaniah, bad u Johanan u khun u Kariah, bad u Seraïah u khun u Tanhumeth u nong Netophath, bad u Jaasaniah u khun u nong Maakath, ma ki bad ki briew jong ki.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te u Gedalaïah u la smai ha ki bad ha ki briew jong ki, bad u la ong ha ki, “Wat sheptieng na ka bynta ki shakri ki Khaldi: to shong ha ka ri, bad to shakri ïa u syiem ka Babilon, te kan long bha bad phi.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hynrei, ha u bnai u bahynñiew, u Ishmael u khun u Nethaniah, u khun u Elishama, uba na ka jaid syiem, u la wan, bad shiphew ngut ki rangbah lem bad u, bad u la pom ïa u Gedalaïah, haduh ba u la ïap, bad ïa ki Jiw bad ïa ki Khaldi kiba bad u ha Mispah.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te u paidbah baroh, u barit bad u bakhraw, bad ki kaptan ki shipai, ki la ïaïeng joit, bad ki la wan sha Ijipt: naba ki la sheptieng ïa ki Khaldi.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te ha ka snem ka balaiphew hynñiew ka jinglongmraw u Jehoïakhin u syiem ka Judah, ha u bnai u bakhat-ar, ha ka sngi ka ba-arphew hynñiew jong uta u bnai, u Ebil-merodak u syiem ka Babilon, ha ka snem ha kaba u la sdang ban synshar, u la kyntiew ïa ka khlieh u Jehoïakhin u syiem ka Judah na ka ïing byndi;",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> bad u la kren sngewbha ïa u, bad u la buh ïa ka khet jong u halor ka khet ki syiem kiba la don bad u ha Babilon;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> bad u la pli ïa ki jaiñ byndi jong u, bad u la bam jingbam ha khmat jong u borabor baroh ki sngi ka jingim jong u.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te ïa ka bynta jong u, ka bynta kaba borabor la ju ai ha u da u syiem, man la ka sngi shi bynta, baroh ki sngi ka jingim jong u."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;